## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-159">Autentifikācijas notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-159">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-160">Šie diagnostikas datu notikumi tiek apkopoti, kad Office mēģina iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai nu nemanāmi vai izmantojot uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-160">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroidmsaguesttoaad"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-162">Šis notikums palīdz izprast, cik daudziem lietotajiem tiek lūgts norādīt personiskā konta paroli, piekļūstot darba resursiem, jo viņu personiskais konts var būt derīgs darbam ar konta nomnieku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-162">This event helps in understanding how many users are getting prompted for providing personal account password, while accessing work resource, as their personal account could be a valid guest to work account's tenant.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-163">Šie dati palīdz mums saprast, cik daudziem lietotajiem ir jāsaskaras ar atkārtotām pieteikšanās uzvednēm, lai prioritizētu nemanāmu AAD marķieru iegūšanu balstoties uz Microsoft konta SAML (drošības novērtējuma iezīmēšanas valoda) vērtējumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-163">This data helps us understand how many users are going through the pain of sign in re-prompts to prioritize AAD token acquisition silently based on a Microsoft account SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) assertion.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-164">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-164">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-165">**Tag** — norāda, ka lietotājs, piekļūstot darba resursam, saņēma pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-165">**Tag** - Indicates that user got sign-in prompt for personal account, while accessing work account resource.</span></span>


### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-167">Tiek apkopots, kad Office rāda lietotājam uz veidlapām balstītas pierakstīšanās uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-167">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-168">Kopā ar kluso pilnvaru iegūšanu autentifikācijas uzvednes tiek izmantotas, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī, kas lietotājam izraisa būtisku bezsaistes klienta stāvokli, vai sliktākajā gadījumā bojāta autentifikācija var traucēt licences iegūšanu, kā arī izraisīt pilnībā nelietojamu klientu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-168">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts are used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-169">Uz veidlapām balstītās autentifikācijas (FBA) pierakstīšanās uzvednes tiek izmantotas dažiem lokāliem autentifikācijas scenārijiem, un parasti mēs vēlamies nodrošināt, ka tā nenotiek, jo visiem vajadzētu lietot moderno autentifikāciju ar FBA saistīto drošības ievainojamību dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-169">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn't happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-170">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-170">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-171">**AuthScheme** — izmantotā autentifikācijas shēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-171">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-172">**DocumentUrlHash** — šifrēta URL pieprasīšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-172">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-173">**EndTag** — tags, kur FBA veidlapa tiek aizpildīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-173">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-174">**Flags** — novecojis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-174">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-175">**FlowTag** — tags, kur FBA veidlapa tiek startēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-175">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-176">**LastError** — atgrieztais kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-176">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-177">**PromptEndTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tika beigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-177">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-178">**PromptStartTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tiek sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-178">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-179">**Result** — vai autentifikācija izdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-179">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-180">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-180">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-181">**Timeout** — laiks, kad uzvednei iestājās taimauts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-181">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-183">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs izrakstās no Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-183">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-184">Zinot, ka lietotājs ir izrakstījies, kļūst iespējams klasificēt citus notikumus, piemēram, uzvednes, kā paredzēts, lai šos notikumus varētu pareizi skaitļot uzticamības/gatavības nosūtīšanai metrikā, kā arī izvairīties no brīdinājumiem vai būvējumu atrites kļūdainā iekārtā, kur lietotājam rodas neparedzētas pierakstīšanās uzvednes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-184">Knowing the user is signed out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-185">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-185">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-186">**FlowEndTime** — laiks, kad izrakstīšanās darbība beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-186">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-187">**FlowStartTime** — laiks, kad izrakstīšanās darbība sākās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-187">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-188">**IdentityErrorState** — jebkāds identitātes kļūdas stāvoklis izrakstīšanās laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-188">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** — šifrētais identitātes ID, kam tiek veikta izrakstīšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-190">**IdentityProviderType** — tās identitātes nodrošinātājs, kurai tiek veikta izrakstīšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-190">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-191">**IdentityUniqueID** — identitātes ID, kam tiek veikta izrakstīšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-191">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-192">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-192">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-193">**SignOutUserAction** — norāda, ka lietotājs sāk izrakstīšanās darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-193">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-195">Tiek apkopots, kad Office rāda lietotājam Windows SSPI pierakstīšanās uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-195">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-196">Kopā ar kluso pilnvaru iegūšanu autentifikācijas uzvednes nosaka, vai lietotājs ir bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī, kas izraisa bezsaistes klienta stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-196">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-197">Bojāta autentifikācija var traucēt licences iegūšanu, kā arī izraisīt pilnībā nelietojamu klientu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-197">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-198">Windows SSPI uzvednes tiek izmantotas autentifikācijai ar Exchange (pasta sinhronizēšanai), ja lietotāja Exchange resurss nav iestatīts daudzfaktoru autentifikācijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-198">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been set up for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-199">Šie notikumi kopā ar Office.MATS nosaukumvietas notikumiem tiek izmantoti tālāk norādītajiem mērķiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-199">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-200">1.\) Identificēt, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-200">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-201">2.\) Novērtēt, vai izmaiņas, kas radušās klientā vai pakalpojumos, ir izraisījušas kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-201">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-202">3.\) Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-202">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-203">4.\) Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus, lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko lietotāju bloķēšanas kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-203">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-204">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-204">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-205">**AllowSavedCreds** — vai jaunie akreditācijas dati ir pastāvīgi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-205">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-206">**AuthScheme** — izmantotā autentifikācijas shēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-206">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-207">**CredsSaved** — vai jaunie akreditācijas dati ir saglabāti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-207">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-208">**DocumentUrlHash** — šifrētā URL pieprasīšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-208">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-209">**EndTag** — tags, kur uzvedne beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-209">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState — vai jaunā identitāte ir derīga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** — šifrētais jaunais identitātes ID pēc uzvednes pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** — jaunais identitātes nodrošinātājs pēc uzvednes pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** — jaunais identitātes ID pēc uzvednes pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-214">**OutStatus** — vai uzvednes izvade ir derīga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-214">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-215">**PromptEndTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tika beigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-215">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-216">**PromptFailedTag** — tags, kas norāda SSPI uzvednes kļūmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-216">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-217">**PromptFlow** — tags, kas izsauca SSPI uzvedni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-217">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-218">**PromptStartTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tiek sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-218">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-219">**Proxy** — vai tiek izmantots starpniekserveris</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-219">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-220">**ServerHash** — šifrētā servera adrese</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-220">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-221">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-221">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-222">**Timeout** — laiks, kad uzvednei iestājas taimauts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-222">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-223">**UiMessage** — UI ziņojums uzvednē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-223">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-224">**UserNameHash** — šifrētais lietotājvārds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-224">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-226">Tiek apkopots, kad Office rāda lietotājam daudzfaktoru autentifikācijas pierakstīšanās uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-226">Collected when Office shows the user a multi-factor authentication sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-227">Kopā ar kluso pilnvaru iegūšanu autentifikācijas uzvednes nosaka, vai lietotājs ir bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī, kas izraisa bezsaistes klienta stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-227">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-228">Bojāta autentifikācija var traucēt licences iegūšanu, kā arī izraisīt pilnībā nelietojamu klientu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-228">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-230">1.\) Identificēt, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-230">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered in to a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-232">3.\) Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-232">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-233">4.\) Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus, lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko lietotāju bloķēšanas kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-233">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-234">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-234">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-235">**AdalWAMUsed** — tags, kas norāda rezultātu, ja tiek izmantots ADAL-atop-WAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – the tag that indicates result if ADAL-atop-WAM is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-236">**CallTag** — tags, kas norāda pierakstīšanās UI izsaucēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-236">**CallTag** – the tag that indicates the caller of sign in UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** — tags, kur tiek pieprasīts identitātes nodrošinātājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** - the tag where the identity provider is requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-248">**PromptStartTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tiek sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-248">**PromptStartTime** – the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-249">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-249">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-250">**ShowUIResult** — rezultāta kods, kas atgriezts no uzvednes UI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-250">**ShowUIResult** – the result code returned from the prompt UI</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-255">Tālāk norādītais apraksts attiecas gan uz Win32, gan WinRT notikumiem (nosaukums ir atkarīgs no platformas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-255">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-256">Microsoft autentifikācijas telemetrijas sistēma (MATS) tiek apkopota, kad Office mēģina iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai nu nemanāmi vai izmantojot uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-256">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-257">Ja iegūšanas mēģinājumi neizdodas, tiek iekļauta kļūdas informācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-257">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-258">Šie notikumi mūsu lietotājiem sniedz iespēju izvairīties no pāriešanas bojātos autentifikācijas stāvokļos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-258">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-259">1.\) Identificēšana, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-259">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-260">2.\) Novērtēt, kad izmaiņas rodas klientā vai pakalpojumos, vai tās izraisa kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-260">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-261">3.\) Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-261">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-262">4.\) Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus, lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-262">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-263">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-263">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-264">**Actiontype** — kura autentifikācijas bibliotēka tiek izmantota</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-264">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-265">**Appaudience** — vai lietojumprogrammas būvējums ir paredzēts iekšējai vai ārējai lietošanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-265">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-266">**Appforcedprompt** — vai lietojumprogramma ignorēja kešatmiņu un nodrošināja uzvednes rādīšanu piespiedu kārtā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-266">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-267">**Appname** — tās lietojumprogrammas nosaukums, kas veic autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-267">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-268">**Appver** — tās lietojumprogrammas versija, kas veic autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-268">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-269">**Askedforcreds** — vai lietojumprogramma pieprasīja lietotājam ievadīt akreditācijas datus šai darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-269">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-270">**Authoutcome** — vai autentifikācijas mēģinājums izdevās, neizdevās vai tika atcelts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-270">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-271">**Blockingprompt** — vai lietojumprogramma parādīja uzvedni, kur bija nepieciešama lietotāja mijiedarbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-271">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-272">**Correlationid** — GUID, kas tiek izmantots savienošanai ar pakalpojumu datiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-272">**Correlationid** - GUID used for joining with services data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-273">**Count** — notikumu skaits apkopojuma gadījumos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-273">**Count** - Count of events in cases of aggregation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-274">**Data\_accounttype** — patērētāja vai organizācijas konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-274">**Data\_accounttype** - Consumer or organizational account</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-275">**Devicenetworkstate** — vai lietotājs bija tiešsaistē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-275">**Devicenetworkstate** - Was the user online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** — anonīmais ierīces ID, kas tika izmantots, lai mērītu ierīces pieredzi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-277">**Duration** — cik ilga bija autentifikācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-277">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-278">**Duration_Max** — ja šis signāls ir apkopots, tad tas ir jebkura apkopotā notikuma maksimālais ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-278">**Duration_Max** - If this signal is aggregated, the maximum duration of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-279">**Duration_Min** — ja šis signāls ir apkopots, tad tas ir jebkura apkopotā notikuma minimālais ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-279">**Duration_Min** - If this signal is aggregated, the minimum duration of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-280">**Duration_Sum** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, tad tas ir visu apkopoto notikumu ilgumu summa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-280">**Duration_Sum** - If this signal is aggregated, the sum of the durations of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-281">**Endtime** — kad autentifikācijas notikums beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-281">**Endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-282">**Error** — kļūdas kods, ja autentifikācija neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-282">**Error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-283">**Errordescription** — īss kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-283">**Errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-284">**Errorsource** — vai kļūda radās pakalpojumā, autentifikācijas bibliotēkā vai lietojumprogrammā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-284">**Errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-285">**Identityservice** — vai tika izsaukts Microsoft pakalpojuma konts (MSA) vai Azure Active Directory (AAD) pakalpojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-285">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-286">**Interactiveauthcontainer** — kāda veida uzvedne tika rādīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-286">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-287">**Issilent** — vai uzvedne tika rādīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-287">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-288">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** — Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL) versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-288">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** — kļūdas kods, ko raidīja autentifikācijas bibliotēka šim autentifikācijas mēģinājumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** — šim autentifikācijas mēģinājumam izsauktais API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** — Azure Active Directory tās iestādes URL, kas atbildīga par lietotāja autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** — patērētāja/Microsoft pakalpojuma līgums (MSA) attiecībā pret organizāciju/Azure Active Directory (AAD); pašlaik vienmēr AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** — norāda, vai autentifikācija tika pabeigta pakalpojuma pusē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** — norāda, vai ADAL autentifikācijai izmantoja starpnieku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** — norāda starpnieka nosaukumu (piemēram, Windows kontu pārvaldība)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – Tells the name of the broker (for example, Windows Account Management)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** — norāda starpnieka versiju, ja tas tiek izmantots</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** - Tells the version of the broker if used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** — kešatmiņas notikumu skaits, ko ADAL veica, izgūstot marķieri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** - Number of cache events ADAL performed while retrieving token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, maksimālais jebkura apkopotā notikuma kešatmiņas notikumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, minimālais jebkura apkopotā notikuma kešatmiņas notikumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, visu apkopoto notikumu kešatmiņas notikumu summa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the cache events of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** — cik reižu API lasīja no diska kešatmiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** - How many times the API read from the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-302">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena lasīšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-302">Present if there was at least one read.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** — cik reižu diska kešatmiņas lasīšana neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache read failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-304">Ir spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-304">Is present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-305">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** — ADAL kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-305">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-306">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena lasīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-306">Present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-307">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** — sistēmas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-307">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-308">Ir spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena lasīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-308">Is present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-311">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** — cik reižu diska kešatmiņas rakstīšana neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-311">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache-write failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-312">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-312">Present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-313">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** — ADAL kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-313">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-314">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena rakstīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-314">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** — sistēmas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-316">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena rakstīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-316">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** — jauktais AAD lietojumprogrammas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** - Hashed AAD app ID</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** — patiess/aplams norāda, vai marķierim ir pagarināts kalpošanas laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** - True/false telling if the token has an extended lifetime.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** — ja šis signāls ir apkopots, minimālais HTTP izsaukumu skaits, ko ADAL veic jebkuram apkopotajam notikumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** — patiess/aplams norāda, vai ADAL API izdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** - True/false telling if ADAL API succeeded.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** — patiess/aplams norāda, vai ADAL pilnās reģistrēšanas režīms ir iespējots.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** - True/false telling if ADAL full logging mode is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-326">Šie dati tiek reģistrēti tikai lokāli, netiek raidīti telemetrijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-326">This data is only logged locally, not emitted in telemetry.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-345">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_token\_type** — atsvaidzināšanas marķieris (RT) vai vairāku resursu atsvaidzināšanas marķieris (MRRT).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-345">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_token\_type** – Either refresh token (RT) or multi-resource refresh token (MRRT).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-346">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_ui\_event\_count** — uzvedņu skaits, kas tiek rādītas lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-346">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_ui\_event\_count** - Count of prompts shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-347">Var būt klusas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-347">May have been silent.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-348">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_user\_cancel** — patiess/aplams, ja lietotāja interfeisa logs tika atcelts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-348">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_user\_cancel** - True / false if the user interface window was canceled.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-350">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_x\_ms\_request\_id** — papildu pieprasījuma ID, ko HTTP galvenē pakalpojumam nodrošina ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-350">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_x\_ms\_request\_id** – Additional request ID provided in HTTP header to service by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-351">**Platform** — Win32/WinRT/Android/iOS/Mac</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-351">**Platform** - Win32/WinRT/Android/iOS/Mac</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-352">**Promptreasoncorrelationid** — uzvednes gadījumā tas ir cita notikuma korelācijas ID, kas izskaidro, kāpēc lietotājam, iespējams, ir redzama autentifikācijas uzvedne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-352">**Promptreasoncorrelationid** – For prompts, this is the correlation id of another event which explains why the user might be seeing an authentication prompt.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-354">**Scenarioid** — GUID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-354">**Scenarioid** – GUID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-355">Vairāki notikumi var piederēt vienam scenārijam, piemēram, scenārijs var pievienot jaunu kontu, bet pastāv vairākas uzvednes, kas rodas kā daļa no šī scenārija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-355">Multiple events may belong to a single scenario, for example, the scenario may be adding a new account but there are multiple prompts that occur as part of that scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-356">Šis ID nodrošina korelācijas iespējamību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-356">This ID enables correlation to happen.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-357">**Scenarioname** — scenārija nosaukums, kuram pieder šis autentifikācijas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-357">**Scenarioname** – The name of the scenario that this authentication event belongs to.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-358">**Sessionid** — GUID, kas identificē sāknēšanas sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-358">**Sessionid** - GUID identifying the boot session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-359">**Skdver** — MATS klienta SDK versija, kas tiek izmantota, lai radītu šos datus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-359">**Skdver** - Version of MATS client SDK used to produce this data</span></span>

### <a name="officematsoneauthactionmicrosoftofficewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-366">Office.MATS.OneAuth.ActionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-366">Office.MATS.OneAuth.ActionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-367">Microsoft autentifikācijas telemetrijas sistēma (MATS) tiek apkopota, kad Office mēģina iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai nu nemanāmi vai izmantojot uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-367">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-368">Ja iegūšanas mēģinājumi neizdodas, tiek iekļauta kļūdas informācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-368">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-369">Šie notikumi mūsu lietotājiem sniedz iespēju izvairīties no pāriešanas bojātos autentifikācijas stāvokļos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-369">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

1) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-370">Identificēšana, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri no pakalpojuma vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-370">Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token from the service, or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

2) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-371">Novērtēt, kad izmaiņas rodas klientā vai pakalpojumos, vai tās izraisa kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-371">Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

3) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-372">Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-372">When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

4) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-373">Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus, lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-373">These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-374">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-374">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-375">**Accounttype** — šim autentifikācijas notikumam izmantotais konta tips, piemēram, patērētājs vai organizācijas konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-375">**Accounttype** - Type of the account used for this authentication event, for example, consumer or organizational.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-376">**Actionname** — draudzīgs nosaukums šim notikumam, ja tāds tika norādīts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-376">**Actionname** - Friendly name for this event, if one was provided.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-377">**Actiontype** — norāda, kāda veida autentifikācijas bibliotēku izmantojat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-377">**Actiontype** - Specifies the type of authentication library in use.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-378">**Appaudience** — vai lietojumprogrammas būvējums ir paredzēts iekšējai vai ārējai lietošanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-378">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-379">**Appforcedprompt** — vai lietojumprogramma ignorēja kešatmiņu un nodrošināja uzvednes rādīšanu piespiedu kārtā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-379">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-380">**Appname** — tās lietojumprogrammas nosaukums, kas veic autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-380">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-381">**Appver** — tās lietojumprogrammas versija, kas veic autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-381">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-382">**Askedforcreds** — vai lietojumprogramma pieprasīja lietotājam ievadīt akreditācijas datus šai darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-382">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-383">**Authoutcome** — vai autentifikācijas mēģinājums izdevās, neizdevās vai tika atcelts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-383">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-384">**Blockingprompt** — vai lietojumprogramma parādīja uzvedni, kur bija nepieciešama lietotāja mijiedarbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-384">**Blockingprompt** -  Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-385">**Correlationid** — identifikators, ko izmanto, lai saistītu informāciju par šo atsevišķo notikumu ar pakalpojumu datiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-385">**Correlationid** - Identifier used to join information regarding this individual event with services data</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-386">**Count** — kopējais apkopoto darbību skaits, kas ziņots šajā vienā datu notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-386">**Count** - The total number of aggregated actions reported in this one data event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-387">**Devicenetworkstate** — vai ierīce ir savienota ar internetu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-387">**Devicenetworkstate** - Is the device connected to the internet.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-388">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** — anonīms ierīces ID, ko izmanto, lai mērītu visas ierīces autentifikācijas pieredzi un uzticamību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-388">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device-wide authentication experience and reliability.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-389">**Duration** — cik ilga bija autentifikācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-389">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-390">**duration_max** — maksimālais jebkura no apkopotajiem notikumiem ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-390">**duration_max** - Max duration of any one of the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-391">**duration_min** — minimālais jebkura no apkopotajiem notikumiem ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-391">**duration_min** - Min duration of any one of the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-392">**duration_sum** — visu apkopoto notikumu ilguma summa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-392">**duration_sum** - Sum of the duration of all the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-393">**endtime** — kad autentifikācijas notikums beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-393">**endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-394">**error** — kļūdas kods, ja autentifikācija neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-394">**error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-395">**errordescription** — īss kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-395">**errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-396">**errorsource** — vai kļūda radās pakalpojumā, autentifikācijas bibliotēkā vai lietojumprogrammā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-396">**errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-397">**eventtype** — vai šis notikums ziņo par autentifikācijas datu punktu vai datu kvalitātes kļūdas notikumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-397">**eventtype** - Is this event reporting an authentication datapoint, or a data quality error event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-398">Izmanto datu kvalitātes mērīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-398">Used to measure data quality.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-399">**from_cache** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai ieraksts ir no WAM kodola kešatmiņas vai spraudņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-399">**from_cache** - Boolean representing whether the record is from the WAM core cache, or the plugin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-400">**hasadaltelemetry** — norāda, vai Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL) nodrošināja šim notikumam telemetriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-400">**hasadaltelemetry** - Indicates whether the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL) provided telemetry for this event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-401">**Identityservice** — vai tika izsaukts Microsoft pakalpojuma konts (MSA) vai Azure Active Directory (AAD) pakalpojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-401">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-402">**Interactiveauthcontainer** — kāda veida uzvedne tika rādīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-402">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-403">**Issilent** — vai tika parādīta uzvedne vai arī šis bija kluss (fona) autentifikācijas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-403">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown or was this a silent (background) authentication event.</span></span>

### <a name="officematsoneauthtransactionmicrosoftofficewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-571">Office.MATS.OneAuth.TransactionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-571">Office.MATS.OneAuth.TransactionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-572">Microsoft autentifikācijas telemetrijas sistēma (MATS) tiek apkopota, kad Office mēģina iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai nu nemanāmi vai izmantojot uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-572">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-573">Šis notikums ir viena vai vairāku ActionMicrosoftOffice notikumu vecākobjekts, kas ļauj apvienot saistītus notikumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-573">This event is a parent of one or more ActionMicrosoftOffice events, allowing related events to be grouped together.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-574">Šie notikumi mūsu lietotājiem sniedz iespēju izvairīties no pāriešanas bojātos autentifikācijas stāvokļos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-574">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

1) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-575">Identificēšana, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri no pakalpojuma vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-575">Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token from the service, or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

2) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-576">Novērtēt, kad izmaiņas rodas klientā vai pakalpojumos, vai tās izraisa kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-576">Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

3) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-577">Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-577">When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

4) <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-578">Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus, lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-578">These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-579">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-579">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-580">**Actiontype** — "oneauthtransaction" ir vienīgā vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-580">**Actiontype** - "oneauthtransaction" is the only value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-581">**Appaudience** — lietojumprogrammu auditorija (automatizācija, priekšražošana vai ražošana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-581">**Appaudience** - Application audience (Automation, Preproduction, or Production)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-582">**Appname** — lietojumprogrammas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-582">**Appname** - App name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-583">**Appver** — lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-583">**Appver** - App version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-584">**Authoutcome** — vai autentifikācijas mēģinājums izdevās, neizdevās vai tika atcelts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-584">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-585">**Correlationid** — identifikators, ko izmanto, lai saistītu informāciju par šo atsevišķo notikumu ar pakalpojumu datiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-585">**Correlationid** - Identifier used to join information regarding this individual event with services data</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-586">**Count** — kļūdas rašanās reižu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-586">**Count** - Number of times the error occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-587">**Devicenetworkstate** — ierīces tīkla stāvoklis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-587">**Devicenetworkstate** - Device network state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-588">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** — ierīces profila telemetrijas ID (virkne, ko MATS izmanto, lai identificētu konkrētu ierīci)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-588">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Device profile telemetry ID (string used by MATS to identify a specific device)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-589">**duration_max** — šajā signālā apkopoto darījumu minimālais ilgums milisekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-589">**duration_max** - Minimum duration, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-590">**duration_min** — šajā signālā apkopoto darījumu maksimālais ilgums milisekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-590">**duration_min** - Maximum duration, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-591">**duration_sum** — šajā signālā apkopoto darījumu ilgumu summa milisekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-591">**duration_sum** - Sum of durations, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-592">**Endtime** — laiks, kurā beidzās OneAuth transakcija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-592">**Endtime** - Time at which the OneAuth transaction ended.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-593">**Error** — OneAuth statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-593">**Error** - OneAuth status code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-594">**Eventtype** — notikuma tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-594">**Eventtype** - Event type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-595">**Issilent** — aplams, ja tika parādīts lietotāja interfeiss; tiesa, ja tas būtu fona notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-595">**Issilent** - False if UI was shown; true if it was a background event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-596">**oneauth_api** — norāda publiski izmantoto OneAuth API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-596">**oneauth_api** - Specifies the public API of OneAuth that was invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-597">**oneauth_Domain** — ja API izsaukums izraisīja kļūdu, šis ir kļūdas sistēmas domēns.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-597">**oneauth_Domain** - If the API call resulted in an error, this is the system domain of that error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-598">**oneauth_ErrorCode** — kļūdas kods, kas attēlo OneAuth iekšējo kļūdas stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-598">**oneauth_ErrorCode** - Error code representing the internal error state for OneAuth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-599">Aizstāj veco lauku oneauth_errortag.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-599">Replaces the old oneauth_errortag field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-600">**oneauth_errortag** — skaitliskais identifikators koda rindai, kas bija atbildīga par kļūdas radīšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-600">**oneauth_errortag** - Numerical identifier for a line of code that was responsible for generating an error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-601">**oneauth_ExecutionFlow** — atzīmju sērija, kas identificē kodēšanas ceļu, kuru šis API izsaukums izmantoja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-601">**oneauth_ExecutionFlow** - A series of tags identifying the codepath this API invocation took.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-602">**oneauth_internalerror** — kļūdas kods, kas attēlo OneAuth iekšējo kļūdas stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-602">**oneauth_internalerror** - Error code representing the internal error state for OneAuth.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-603">**oneauth_ServerErrorCode** — servera kļūda, kas tiek atgriezta OneAuth, šī API zvana noslēgumā, ja tāda tika konstatēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-603">**oneauth_ServerErrorCode** - The server error returned to OneAuth at the conclusion of this API call, if one was encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-604">**oneauth_SystemErrorCode** — sistēmas kļūda, kas tiek atgriezta OneAuth, šī API zvana noslēgumā, ja tāda tika konstatēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-604">**oneauth_SystemErrorCode** - The system error returned to OneAuth at the conclusion of this API call, if one was encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-605">**oneauth_Tag** — OneAuth marķieris, kas norāda galīgo vietu kodā, tika sasniegts šī API zvana beigās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-605">**oneauth_Tag** - The OneAuth tag designating the final place in code reached at the conclusion of this API call.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-606">**oneauth_transactionuploadid** — norāda nejauši ģenerētu iekšējo GUID, kas kartē konkrētu OneAuth API izsaukumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-606">**oneauth_transactionuploadid** - Specifies the randomly generated internal GUID that maps to the specific invocation of a OneAuth API.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-607">**oneauth_version** — OneAuth SDK versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-607">**oneauth_version** - The version of the OneAuth SDK.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-608">**Platformu** — operētājsistēmas platforma (0: Win32, 1: Android, 2: iOS, 3: macOS, 4: WinRT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-608">**Platform** - OS Platform (0: Win32, 1: Android, 2: iOS, 3: macOS, 4: WinRT</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-609">**Scenarioname** — scenārija nosaukums, kuram nepieciešama autentifikācija, ko nosaka izsaucošā lietojumprogramma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-609">**Scenarioname** - Name of the scenario for which auth is necessary, specified by the calling application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-610">**Schemaver** — shēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-610">**Schemaver** - Schema Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-611">**Sdkver** — MATS SDK versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-611">**Sdkver** - Version of the MATS sdk</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsaccountfound"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-618">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-618">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-619">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, ja tiek atrasts derīgs atsvaidzināšanas marķieris kontu sarakstā, ko nodrošina TokenSharingManager.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-619">This event is logged when an account with a valid refresh token is found among the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-620">Šis scenārijs attiecas uz vienoto pierakstīšanos (SSO).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-620">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO).</span></span>
