## <a name="click-to-run-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-635">Click-to-Run notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-635">Click-to-Run events</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunbootstrapper"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-636">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-636">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-637">Office iestatīšanas un krājumu dati, kas tiek apkopoti, kad lietotājs palaiž failu Office setup.exe, lai modificētu savus instalētos Office produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-637">Office set up and inventory data collected when the user is running Office setup.exe to modify their installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-638">Tiek izmantots, lai mērītu pilnas lietotāja uzsāktas Office instalēšanas sekmīgu izpildi/kļūmi, tostarp priekšnoteikumu pārbaudes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-638">Used to measure success / failure of a full user-initiated Office installation including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-639">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-639">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-640">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** — kļūdas kods, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-640">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-641">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** — funkcija, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-641">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-642">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** — daļa, kas neizdevās boostrapperbootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-642">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – The part that we failed in the boostrapperbootstrapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-643">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** — izņēmuma veids, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-643">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-644">**Data\_Culture** — kultūra, ar kuru izmantojam šo exe failu, t.i., en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-644">**Data\_Culture** - the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-645">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** — marķiera sha-256 jaukšanas vērtība, ko OLS pakalpojums mums piešķir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-645">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** - a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-646">**Data\_Platform** — x64 vai x86 instalācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-646">**Data\_Platform** - x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-647">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** — priekšnoteikumu kļūme, kāda rodas, t.i., operētājsistēma netiek atbalstīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-647">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – The prerequisite failure we hit, i.e. the operating system is not supported</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-648">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** — produkts, ko instalējam, piemēram, Microsoft 365 programmas lieluzņēmumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-648">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruncorruptioncheck"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-649">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-649">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-650">Office iestatīšanas un krājumu dati, kas tiek apkopoti, kad Click-to-Run klients veic bojājumu pārbaudi, lai nodrošinātu, ka Office binārie faili ir pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-650">Office set up and inventory data collected when Click-to-Run client is running a corruption check to make sure that Office binaries are correct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-651">Tiek izmantots, lai mērītu Office bināro failu bojājumu un to, kuri binārie faili ir bojāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-651">Used to measure corruption of Office binaries, and which binaries are corrupt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-652">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-652">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-653">**Data\_Active —** pašreizējais straumes manifests, ko pārbaudām diskā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-653">**Data\_Active -** The current stream manifest we're checking on disk</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-654">**Data\_ActivePackages —** kādas pakotnes manifests satur</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-654">**Data\_ActivePackages -** what packages the manifest contains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-655">**Data\_ActiveVersion —** manifesta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-655">**Data\_ActiveVersion -** the version of the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-656">**Data\_AddFileCount —** cik failu pievienojam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-656">**Data\_AddFileCount -** how many files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-657">**Data\_AddFileFiles —** failu, ko pievienojam, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-657">**Data\_AddFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-658">**Data\_CompressionLevel —** kā faili tiek saspiesti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-658">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-659">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel —** cik dziļi meklējam bojājumus, pakāpes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-659">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel -** how deeply we're checking for corruption, stages</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-660">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount —** cik failiem ir bojāts lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-660">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount -** how many files have a corrupt size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-661">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles —** failu, kam ir bojāts lielums, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-661">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-662">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount —** cik failiem ir bojāta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-662">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount -** how many files have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-663">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles —** failu, kam ir bojāta versija, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-663">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-664">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount —** cik failus neizdevās atvērt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-664">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount -** how many files we failed to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-665">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles —** failu, ko nevaram atvērt, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-665">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles -** a sample of the files that we were unable to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-666">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount —** cik faili nav parakstīti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-666">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount -** have many files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-667">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles —** failu, kas nav parakstīti, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-667">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles -** a sample of the files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-668">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount —** cik faili nav uzticami</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-668">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount -** how many files aren't trusted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-669">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles —** failu, kam neuzticamies, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-669">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles -** a sample of the files that we don't trust</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-670">**Data\_IncompleteFileCount —** cik faili šķiet nepilnīgi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-670">**Data\_IncompleteFileCount -** how many files seem to be incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-671">**Data\_IncompleteFileFiles —** nepilnīgo failu paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-671">**Data\_IncompleteFileFiles -** a sample of the files that are incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-672">**Data\_KeepFileCount —** ar cik failiem neko nedarām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-672">**Data\_KeepFileCount -** how many files we're not doing anything to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-673">**Data\_KeepFileFiles —** failu, ko paturam, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-673">**Data\_KeepFileFiles -** a sample of files we're keeping</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-674">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileCount —** cik failus nemainām, neskatoties uz to, ka tie ir nepilnīgi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-674">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileCount -** how many files we're not changing despite them being incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-675">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileFiles —** failu, ko paturam un kuri ir nepilnīgi, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-675">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're keeping that are incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-676">**Data\_MismatchSizeCount —** cik failu izmērs neatbilst mūsu manifestam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-676">**Data\_MismatchSizeCount -** how many files have a size that doesn't match our manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-677">**Data\_MismatchSizeFiles —** failu, kam ir neatbilstošs lielums, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-677">**Data\_MismatchSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that are mismatched in size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-678">**Data\_MismatchVersionCount —** cik failiem versija atšķiras no mūsu manifesta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-678">**Data\_MismatchVersionCount -** how many files that have a version different than our manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-679">**Data\_MismatchVersionFiles —** failu, kam ir neatbilstošas versijas, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-679">**Data\_MismatchVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have mismatched versions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-680">**Data\_MissingFileCount —** cik failu trūkst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-680">**Data\_MissingFileCount -** how many files seem to be missing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-681">**Data\_MissingFileFiles —** trūkstošo failu paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-681">**Data\_MissingFileFiles -** a sample of the files that are missing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-682">**Data\_NotToBeStreamedFileCount —** cik failus nestraumējam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-682">**Data\_NotToBeStreamedFileCount -** how many files we're not streaming</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-683">**Data\_RemoveFileCount —** cik failu noņemam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-683">**Data\_RemoveFileCount -** how many files we're removing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-684">**Data\_RemoveFileFiles —** failu, ko noņemam, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-684">**Data\_RemoveFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're removing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-685">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchCount —** cik failiem ir vienības, kas neatbilst manifestam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-685">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchCount -** how many files have units that don't match the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-686">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchFiles —** failu, kam ir straume ar neatbilstošām vienībām, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-686">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchFiles -** a sample of the files that have a stream with units mismatched</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-687">**Data\_TimeElapsed —** cik ilga bija bojājumu meklēšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-687">**Data\_TimeElapsed -** how long we took to check for corruption</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-688">**Data\_UpdateFileCount —** cik failu atjauninām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-688">**Data\_UpdateFileCount -** how many files we're updating</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-689">**Data\_UpdateFileFiles —** failu, ko pievienojam, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-689">**Data\_UpdateFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-690">**Data\_Working —** jaunais manifests, ko pārbaudām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-690">**Data\_Working -** the new manifest we're checking</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-691">**Data\_WorkingVersion —** jaunā manifesta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-691">**Data\_WorkingVersion -** the version of the new manifest</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunmachinemetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-692">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-692">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunodt"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-700">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-700">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-701">Office iestatīšanas un krājumu dati, kas tiek apkopoti, kad IT administrators palaiž Office izvietošanas rīka Click-to-Run failu setup.exe, lai modificētu savu lietotāju instalētos Office produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-701">Office set up and inventory data collected when an IT Admin is running the Office Deployment Tool Click-to-Run setup.exe to modify their users' installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-702">Tie tiek izmantoti, lai mērītu pilnas IT administratora uzsāktas Office instalēšanas sekmīgu izpildi/kļūmi, tostarp priekšnoteikumu pārbaudes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-702">It is used to measure success / failure of full IT Admin initiated Office installations including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-703">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-703">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-708">**Data\_ConfigurationHost —** resursdators, no kura nācis fails configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-708">**Data\_ConfigurationHost-** The host where the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-712">**Data\_HashedOLSToken —** marķiera sha-256 jaukšanas vērtība, ko OLS pakalpojums mums piešķir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-712">**Data\_HashedOLSToken-** a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-720">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-720">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-721">Ziņo par jaunā Click-to-Run atjauninājumu konveijera statusu (“Repoman”) un par to, vai tas veiksmīgi lejupielādē un instalē Office atjauninājumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-721">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline ("Repoman") and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-722">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-722">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-723">**ApplySucceeded —** patiess, ja konveijers veiksmīgi lietoja Office atjauninājumu, pretējā gadījumā — aplams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-723">**ApplySucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully applied an Office update, false if not.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-724">**DownloadSucceeded —** patiess, ja konveijers veiksmīgi lietoja Office atjauninājumu, pretējā gadījumā — aplams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-724">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-725">**ErrorCode —** pēdējās kļūdas kods, kura radās Click-to-Run Repoman konveijerā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-725">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-726">**ErrorDetails —** papildu informācija par kļūdu, kura radās Click-to-Run Repoman konveijerā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-726">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-727">**ErrorMessage —** pēdējās kļūdas ziņa, kura radās Click-to-Run Repoman konveijerā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-727">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-728">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded —** patiess, ja konveijerā veiksmīgi tiek radīta sesija Office atjauninājuma straumēšanai, pretējā gadījumā — aplams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-728">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-729">**RepomanErrorMessage —** kļūdas ziņojums, kurš saņemts no repoman.dll.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-729">**RepomanErrorMessage -** The error message received from the repoman.dll.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1793">**CMDMode —** draudzīgā virkne, kas atbilst tam, kāds vispārējā režīma pārslēgs tika noteikts .exe failam nodotajos cmd argumentos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1793">**CMDMode –**    The friendly string corresponding to which overall mode switch was detected in the cmd arguments passed to the exe.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1794">Iespējas ir: automātiskā palaišana, konfigurēšana, patērētājs, lejupielāde, palīdzība, pakotājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1794">Possibilities are:  autorun, configure, consumer, download, help, packager</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1795">**DeliveryMechanism —** “FFNRoot” GUID, kas izvilkts no versijas deskriptora XML faila (apzīmogots ar RDX), kurš norāda, no kuras auditorijas/kanāla ir nācis būvējuma avots</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1795">**DeliveryMechanism –**    The "FFNRoot" guid extracted from the Version Descriptor XML (stamped by RDX), which tells us which audience/channel the build source came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1796">**DownloadC2RClientAction —** “patiess”, ja šīs instalēšanas laikā ir ieplānota uzdevuma DownloadC2RClientAction izpilde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1796">**DownloadC2RClientAction –**    "true" if the DownloadC2RClientAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1797">**ErrorCode —** vesels skaitlis, kas saistīts ar neapstrādātu izņēmumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1797">**ErrorCode –**    Integer value associated with an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1798">**ErrorDetails —** virkne, kas apraksta atrašanās vietu, kur radās neapstrādāts izņēmums (funkcija, fails, rindiņas numurs, metēja iestatītie papildu parametri)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1798">**ErrorDetails –**    String that describes the location of where an unhandled exception occurred (function, file, line number, additional parameters set by the thrower)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1799">**ErrorMessage —** virkne, kas definēta punktā, kurā tika izmests neapstrādāts izņēmums, aprakstot kļūmes būtību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1799">**ErrorMessage –**    String defined at the point where an unhandled exception was thrown, describing the nature of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1800">**ErrorType —** virkne, kas apraksta neapstrādāta izņēmuma kategoriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1800">**ErrorType –**    String describing the category of an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1801">**ExitCode —** vesela skaitļa vērtība, kas saistīta ar sāknēšanas programmas izpildes fāzes darbības rezultātu, norādot sekmes vai konkrētus kļūmju tipus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1801">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the Execute phase of the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1802">**LaunchAction —** “patiess”, ja šīs instalēšanas laikā ir ieplānota uzdevuma LaunchAction izpilde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1802">**LaunchAction –**    "true" if the LaunchAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1803">**LaunchUpdateAction —** “patiess”, ja šīs instalēšanas laikā ir ieplānota uzdevuma LaunchUpdateAction izpilde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1803">**LaunchUpdateAction –**    "true" if the LaunchUpdateAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1804">**PreReqResult —** rezultāta vesela skaitļa uzskaitījuma vērtība, ja tika veiktas PreReq pārbaudes (izturēja/neizturēja/atkārtota palaišana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1804">**PreReqResult –**    The integer enum value of the result when PreReq checks were performed (pass/fail/re-run)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1805">**UnexpectedAction —**“patiess”, ja uzdevumam UnexpectedAction (kļūdas gadījums) ir ieplānota veikšana šīs instalēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1805">**UnexpectedAction –**    "true" if the UnexpectedAction task (an error case) is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1806">**VersionToInstall —** instalējamās Office versijas virknes vērtība formātā “16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1806">**VersionToInstall –**    String value of the Office "16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy" version that is being installed</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1807">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1807">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1808">*[Šis notikums ir dzēsts jaunākajos Office būvējumos, taču, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1808">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1809">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai iegūtu standarta metadatus par katru inventāra pievienojumprogrammas darbību, kas ir daļa no tehniskās apkopes pārvaldnieka un tiek izmantota Office informācijas uzskaitei datoros un ierīcēs, kurām administrators to ir iespējojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1809">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1810">Šeit īpaši interesanti sesijas ID metadati, kas tiek izmantoti, lai izveidotu saiti uz citiem datiem, kas ir saglabāti katra nomnieka mākoņa pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1810">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1811">Šis notikums nesatur ekstra laukus, jo saistoši ir tikai metadati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1811">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1812">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1812">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1813">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, kad izsaukums uz tīmekļa pakalpojumu, kas veikts, izmantojot noklikšķināt, lai palaistu funkcionālo darbību pievienojumprogrammu, tiek pabeigts, neatkarīgi no tā, vai tas ir sekmīgs vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1813">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1814">Tā būtībā ir pēdējā operācija pievienojumprogrammā, lai izsekotu kopējo darbības statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1814">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1815">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1815">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1816">**ActionDetail** — papildu detalizēta informācija, kad rodas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1816">**ActionDetail** -  Additional details for when a failure occurs.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1817">Ja HTTP pieprasījums izdodas, ActionDetail būs 0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1817">If the HTTP request succeeds, ActionDetail will be 0.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1818">Ja rezultāta lauks nav labs (t.i., nav 0), tas nozīmē, ka pieprasījums netiek nosūtīts, šis lauks reģistrēs iekšējās kļūdas kodu, kas ir tāds pats kā Rezultāta lauks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1818">If the Result field is not OK (i.e. not 0), which means that the request is not sent, this field will log the internal error code which is the same as the Result field.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1819">Ja rezultāts ir labs (t.i., 0), tas nozīmē, ka HTTP atbildes kods >= 300, tas reģistrēs HTTP atbildes kodu (piem., 404).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1819">If the Result field is OK (i.e. 0), which means that the HTTP response code >= 300, it will log the HTTP response code (e.g. 404).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1820">**Result** — skaitlisks kļūdas kodu karodziņi, ko atgriezis Office tīmekļa pakalpojumu zvanu API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1820">**Result** - Numeric error code flags returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1821">– piem., 3 nozīmētu, ka ir radusies problēma ar HTTP galveņu inicializēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1821">– e.g. 3 would mean that there was a problem initializing the HTTP headers.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1822">**Ierakstiet** — papildu informāciju par tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1822">**Type** - Additional type information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1823">Krājuma gadījumā šī informācija norāda, kāda veida vērtumus tiek sūtīts, piem., pilns vai tikai izmaiņu delta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1823">In the case of the Inventory, this information specifies the type of payload being sent – e.g. full or just a delta of changes.</span></span> 

-  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1824">**WebCallSource** — uzskaitījuma vērtība (norādīta kā vesels skaitlis), kas norāda, kāda ir apkalpojamības pārvaldnieka pievienojumprogramma, kas bija zvana avots:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1824">**WebCallSource** - An enumeration value (specified as an integer) indicating the Serviceability Manager add-on that was the source of the call:</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1825">Krājumu saraksts: 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1825">Inventory: 0</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1826">Krājumu konfigurācija: 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1826">Inventory Configuration: 1</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1827">Krājumu politika: 2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1827">Inventory Policy: 2</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1828">Krājumu tīkla statuss: 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1828">Inventory Network Status: 3</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1829">Apkopes pārvaldnieks: 4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1829">Serviceability Manager: 4</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1830">Pārvaldīšanas iespējas: 5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1830">Manageability: 5</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerwebservicefailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1831">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1831">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1832">Šis paziņojums tiek reģistrēts, katru reizi, kad notiek kādas Office tehniskās apkopes pārvaldnieka pievienojumprogrammas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1832">Whenever a call to a webservice within one of the Office Serviceability Manager add-ins fails, this statement is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1833">Kļūmju iemesls var būt iekšējās kļūmes vai nespēja izveidot savienojumu ar tīmekļa pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1833">Failures can be due to internal failures or an inability to connect to the webservice.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1834">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1834">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1835">**Pievienojumprogramma** — noklikšķināt, lai palaistu tehniskās apkopes pārvaldnieka pievienojumprogramma, no kuras tīmekļa pakalpojuma zvans tika veikts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1835">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1836">Tam var būt vērtības, piemēram, krājums, pārvaldāmība utt., kas kodēta kā skaitliska vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1836">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1837">**Korelācijas ID** — nejauši ģenerētu GUID, kas raksturīgs pašreizējai instancei, kas tiek nosūtīta tīmekļa pakalpojumam, lai saistītu zvanus starp klientu un serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1837">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1838">**Result** — skaitliska kļūdas kodu informācija, ko atgriezis Office tīmekļa pakalpojumu zvanu API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1838">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1839">**ErrorMessage** — ziņojums, kas sniedz papildu ieskatu par kļūmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1839">**ErrorMessage** - A message providing further insight into the failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1840">Katrs kļūdas tips tiek kartēts pie stingri kodētas virknes, bet daži kļūdu tipi var būt potenciāli kartēti ar vairākām virknēm, atkarībā no kļūmes specifikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1840">Each error type maps to a hardcoded string, with some error types mapping to potentially multiple strings depending on the specific nature of the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1841">**Funkcija** — funkcija kodā, no kura ir noticis pašreizējais zvans.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1841">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1842">**Statusa** — HTTP statusa kods, ko atgriezis zvans uz tīmekļa pakalpojumu, piemēram, 404, 500 utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1842">**Status** - The HTTP status code returned by the call to the webservice, e.g. 404, 500, etc.</span></span>


## <a name="enhanced-configuration-service-ecs-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1843">Uzlabotās konfigurācijas pakalpojuma (ECS) notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1843">Enhanced Configuration Service (ECS) events</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationflightnumberline"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1850">Office.Experimentation.FlightNumberLine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1850">Office.Experimentation.FlightNumberLine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1851">Apkopo konfigurāciju sarakstu, ko klients saņēmis no ECS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1851">Collects the list of configurations received by the client from ECS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1852">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1852">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1853">**ECSConfigs** — komatatdalīts ECS konfigurāciju saraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1853">**ECSConfigs** - Comma-separated list of ECS Configs</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1854">**LockType** — FlightManager bloķēšanas veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1854">**LockType** - Type of FlightManager lock.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1855">**TasFlightingVersion** — versijas numurs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1855">**TasFlightingVersion** - Version number</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1856">**TimeToLock** — laiks starp liblet uzsākšanu un FlightManager bloķēšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1856">**TimeToLock** - Time between liblet initiation and FlightManager lock</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1857">**UnmergedConfigs** — nesapludināto konfigurāciju saraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1857">**UnmergedConfigs** - List of configurations not merged</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationtriggeranalysis"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1858">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1858">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1859">Šis pasākums palīdz analizēt produktu lietojuma un veiktspējas rādītāju apjomu (piemēram, avārijas, uzkāršanos) lietotāju vai ierīču apakškopā, kura drīkst izmantot līdzekli, nodrošinot pareizu produkta darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1859">This event helps scope analysis of product usage and performance metrics (such as crashes, hangs, etc.) to the subset of users or devices that are eligible to use the feature, thereby helping ensure that the product is working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1860">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1860">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1861">**FeatureGate —** nosaka līdzekļu kopu, kura atbilst cēloņu analīzei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1861">**FeatureGate -** Identifies the set of features for which the trigger analysis is applicable.</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteflightdefault"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1862">OneNote.FlightDefault</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1862">OneNote.FlightDefault</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1863">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, kad OneNote pieprasa ECS serveri lidojuma vērtībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1863">This event is logged when OneNote asks ECS server for flight values.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1864">To var izmantot, lai nodrošinātu eksperimentālus līdzekļus tiem lietotājiem, kuri ir pieteikušies saņemt šādus lidojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1864">This is used to enable experimental features to those users who have opted in for receiving such flights.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1900">Šī produkta telemetrija tiek apkopota, lai izsekotu un uzskaitītu iekšējo transakciju statusu un saskaņošanas informāciju uzticamības un veiktspējas uzlabošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1900">This product telemetry is collected for tracking and logging the internal transaction status and reconciliation information to improve reliability and performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1901">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai analizētu un uzlabotu iekšējo transakciju apstrādes un saskaņošanas mehānismu uzticamību un veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1901">Microsoft uses this data to analyze and improve the reliability and performance of the internal transaction processing and reconciliation mechanisms.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1902">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1902">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1905">**StatusCode** — RFS atbildes statusa kods (RFS definēts uzskaitījums int-ierobežots)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1905">**StatusCode** - RFS response status code (RFS defined Enum int- finite)</span></span>


### <a name="officeandroiddocsuipaywallcontrolseeallfeaturesanalytics"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1906">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SeeAllFeaturesAnalytics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1906">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SeeAllFeaturesAnalytics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1907">Mēs apkopojam šo lietošanas telemetriju, lai redzētu, cik daudz laika lietotājs pavada ekrānā “Skatīt citas priekšrocības”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1907">We collect this usage telemetry to see how much time the user spends on the “See more benefits” screen.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1908">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai izprastu līdzekļa “Skatīt vairāk priekšrocības” lietojumu un optimizētu tā lietošanas pieredzi nākamajās versijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1908">The data is used to understand usage of the “See more benefits” feature and further optimize the experience in future versions.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1912">**MostExplored** — vesels skaitlis, kas apzīmē visvairāk pārslēdzamā vienuma indeksu Microsoft 365 programmu un to līdzekļu sarakstā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1912">**MostExplored** - Integer denoting the index of the most toggled item in a list of Microsoft 365 apps and their features</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1913">**SessionID** — vispārēji unikāls identifikators (GUID), lai savienotu notikumus pēc sesijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1913">**SessionID** - Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) to connect events by session</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroiddocsuiviewsdimeerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1921">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.DimeError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1921">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.DimeError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1922">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammai darbam ar Android (izlaista Huawei un Ķīnas veikalos).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1922">This event is collected for the Office app for Android (released on Huawei and in China Stores).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1923">Šis notikums norāda, ka mēģinājums iegādāties Microsoft 365 abonementu, izmantojot Dime (klienta tīmekļa skatā ielādēts tīmekļa vietrādis URL), neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1923">This event indicates that an attempt to purchase a Microsoft 365 subscription through Dime (a webURL loaded in client webview) has failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1924">Tiek tverti tikai kļūdu scenāriji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1924">Only the error scenarios are captured.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1925">Šī notikuma dati ir tikai kļūdas dati un tie tiek izmantoti, lai nodrošinātu Dime pirkumu plūsmas darbspēju klientā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1925">This event data is error data only and is used to ensure the health of the Dime purchase flow in the client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1926">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1926">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1927">**CorrelationID** — ID, kas unikāli identificē Dime pirkuma sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1927">**CorrelationID** - ID that uniquely identifies a Dime purchase session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1928">**ErrorReason** — norāda kļūdas rašanās iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1928">**ErrorReason** - Indicates the reason for the error that happened.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1929">0 — nezināma kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1929">0 – Unknown error</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1930">1 — internets nav pieejams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1930">1 – Internet not available</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1931">2 — vispārēji unikālā identifikatora (UUID) validācija neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1931">2 – Universally unique identifier (UUID) validation failed</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1932">3 — vispārēji unikāls identifikators (UUID) ir null vai tukšs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1932">3 - Universally unique identifier (UUID) is null or empty</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1933">4 — JavaScript injekcijas kļūda, kur Office lietojumprogramma darbam ar Android nevar padot authToken uz Dime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1933">4 – JavaScript injection error where the Office app for Android can’t pass authToken to Dime</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1934">5 — bāzes tīmekļa URL, kas ielādēts klientā, ir nederīgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1934">5 – Base WebURL loaded on client is invalid</span></span>


### <a name="officeandroiddocsuiviewspremiumfeatureupsell"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1935">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PremiumFeatureUpsell</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1935">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PremiumFeatureUpsell</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1936">Šis notikums uzskaita klikšķus, kurus lietotājs veic, lai skatītu par maksu pieejamu saturu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1936">This event captures clicks by a free user clicks to view a feature behind the pay wall.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1937">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai mērītu lietotāju mijiedarbību ar konteksta pārdošanas līdzekļiem un izprastu, kuriem līdzekļiem lietotāji dod priekšroku, un kuru no šiem līdzekļiem motivē lietotājus iegādāties abonementu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1937">The data is used to measure the interaction of users with the contextual upsell experience and understand which features are preferred by the user which drives them to buy a subscription.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1938">Tas mums palīdz investēt līdzekļus šajos reklāmas punktos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1938">This helps us invest to improve those preferred set of entry points.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1939">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1939">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1940">**featureId** – maksas līdzekļa TCID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1940">**featureId** - TCID for premium feature</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1941">**featureName** – maksas līdzekļa nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1941">**featureName** - Premium Feature Title</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1942">**seePlanButtonClick** – cik reižu papildu pārdošanas izvēlnē tiek noklikšķinātas pogas “Skatīt plānus”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1942">**seePlanButtonClick** - How many times “See plan buttons” gets clicked in upsell UI</span></span>

### <a name="officeappleiapreviewyoursubscriptionios"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1943">Office.Apple.IAPReviewYourSubscriptioniOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1943">Office.Apple.IAPReviewYourSubscriptioniOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1944">Šis notikums uzskaita sesijas meta datus, kad lietotājam tiek parādīta lietojumprogrammas pirkumu (IAP) lietotāja saskarne, un pogas, ar kurām mijiedarbojas lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1944">This event captures session-based metadata when the In-App-Purchase (IAP) UI is shown to the user and the buttons the user subsequently interacts with.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1945">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai palīdzētu mums izprast pirkumu plūsmas aizķeršanās un salīdzināt to ar dažādu iepirkšanās līdzekļu piltuvēm, lai izprastu, kurš no līdzekļiem ir labāks lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1945">This data is used to help us understand the friction in the purchase flow and compare it with the funnel of a different purchase experience to understand which experience is better for the user.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1946">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1946">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1948">**Restore** – virkne – kārtulas atzīme, kas tiek reģistrēta, kad tiek noklikšķināta atjaunošanas poga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1948">**Restore** - String – rule tag is logged when restore button is clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1949">**PremiumFeatures** – virkne – kārtulas atzīme, kas tiek reģistrēta, kad tiek noklikšķināta poga “PremiumFeatures”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1949">**PremiumFeatures** - String – rule tag is logged when “PremiumFeatures” button is clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-1950">**Product** – virkne – lietotāju atlasītā SKU</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-1950">**Product** - String - The SKU selected by the users</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2090">**Acid** — GUID identifikators, kas norāda Office produktu, kuram lietotājam ir licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2090">**Acid** – A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2097">Mēs to apkopojam, kad lietotājs iestata ierīci un mēs izsaucam mūsu licencēšanas pakalpojumu, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājam, kas ir pieteicies, ir Office tiesības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2097">We collect this when the user is setting up a device and we call our licensing service to detect if the logged in user has an Office entitlement or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2098">Tādējādi tiek norādīts attiecīgā izsaukuma rezultāts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2098">This reports the result of that call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2099">Tas ir kritiski svarīgs, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam trūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2099">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2101">**EntitlementCount** — lietotājam piešķirto pilnvaru skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2101">**EntitlementCount** – Number of entitlements the user has</span></span>


### <a name="officelicensingheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2102">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2102">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2103">Katrā sesijā pārbaudām, vai ir pagājušas 72 stundas kopš pēdējās licences atjaunošanas, un mēģinām pagarināt pašreizējās licences derīguma termiņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2103">On every session, we check if 72 hours have passed since the last license renewal and try to extend the expiry of the current license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2104">Šis notikums ziņo par izsaukuma, ko veicam, lai nodrošinātu, ka varam pagarināt licences derīguma termiņu un uzturēt lietotāja Office instalācijas funkcionalitāti, sekmīgu izpildi vai kļūmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2104">This event reports the success or failure of the call that we make to ensure we can extend the expiry of the license and keep the user's Office installation functional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2105">Tas ir kritiski svarīgi, lai diagnosticētu ar abonementu saistītas problēmas un pakalpojumu problēmas lietotājam, kā arī ir kritiski svarīgi, lai noteiktu regresiju jau aktivizēto abonementu lietotājiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2105">It is critical in diagnosing subscription-related issues and service issues for the user and is critical in detecting regressions for already activated subscription users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2107">**Mode** — šajā datorā izmantotā Office licencēšanas steka skaitītāja attēlojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2107">**Mode** – An enumerator representation of the Office licensing stack that is being used on this machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginclientpinredemptioncallpinredemptionapi"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2108">Office.Licensing.InClientPinRedemption.CallPinRedemptionAPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2108">Office.Licensing.InClientPinRedemption.CallPinRedemptionAPI</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2109">Šī telemetrija izseko Office PIN izpirkšanas pakalpojuma zvana rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2109">This telemetry tracks the results of Office's pin redemption service call.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2113">**ErrorType** — kļūmes iemesls, piemēram, "AlreadyRedeemedByOther".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2113">**ErrorType** - Reason of failure, such as "AlreadyRedeemedByOther".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2114">**InAFOFlow** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai mēs esam AFO izpirkšanas plūsmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2114">**InAFOFlow** - A Boolean indicating if we are in the AFO redemption flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2117">**UsingNulApi** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai mēs izmantojam jauno licencēšanas steku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2117">**UsingNulApi** - A Boolean indicating if we are using the new licensing stack.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2119">Ja ierīce pāriet samazinātas funkcionalitātes režīmā, mēs izsūtām šo signālu, lai norādītu, ka iekārta nav darbspējīgā stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2119">If the device enters reduced functionality mode, we send out this signal to indicate that the machine is not in a healthy state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2120">Tas ir kritiski svarīgs, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam trūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2120">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2124">**Mode** — šajā datorā izmantotā Office licencēšanas steka skaitītāja attēlojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2124">**Mode** – An enumerator representation of the Office licensing stack that is being used on this machine</span></span>
