### <a name="officelicensingnulfetcherfetchmodelfromols"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2170">Office.Licensing.Nul.Fetcher.FetchModelFromOls</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2170">Office.Licensing.Nul.Fetcher.FetchModelFromOls</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2171">Ja ierīce izmanto moderno licencēšanas steku, mēģinām iegūt licences failu tieši no pakalpojuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2171">When the device is on the modern licensing stack, we try to get a license file directly from the service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2172">Šis notikums ziņo par sekmīgu izpildi vai kļūmi kopā ar attiecīgā pakalpojuma izsaukuma kļūdas kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2172">This event reports the success or failure along with the error code of that service call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2173">Tas ir kritiski svarīgi, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī modernajā licencēšanas stekā, kas tiek izmantots sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2173">It is critical to detect if the user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2174">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2174">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2175">**MetadataValidationResult** — licences metadatu pārbaudes rezultāts, lai verificētu, ka tā nav ietekmēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2175">**MetadataValidationResult** – Result of the validation of the metadata of the license to verify that it has not been tampered with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2176">**SignatureValidationResult** — licences paraksta pārbaudes rezultāts, lai verificētu, ka tā nav ietekmēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2176">**SignatureValidationResult** – Result of the validation of the signature of the license to verify that it has not been tampered with</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingnulvalidationfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2177">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2177">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2178">Tas tiek apkopots katrā ierīces sesijā, kas darbojas modernajā licencēšanas stekā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2178">This is collected on every session of a device that is running on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2179">Ziņo datora licencēšanas stāvokli un kļūdas, kas lietotājam rodas un kuru dēļ tas nevar izmantot programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2179">It reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2180">Šis notikums norāda, vai lietotāja dators ir darbspējīgs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2180">This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2181">Esam iestatījuši anomāliju noteikšanu šim notikumam, lai norādītu, vai regresija izraisa neatbilstošo lietotāju uzvedību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2181">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2182">Tas ir arī kritiski svarīgi, kad tiek diagnosticētas lietotāja problēmas, kā arī sistēmas darbspējas pārraudzībai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2182">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2183">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2183">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2184">**Acid** — GUID identifikators, kas norāda Office produktu, kuram lietotājam ir licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2184">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2185">**AllAcids** — visu produkta GUID saraksts, kam lietotājam pašlaik ir licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2185">**AllAcids** – List of all the GUIDs of the product that the user is currently licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2186">**Category** — lietotāja izmantotās Office licences kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2186">**Category** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2187">**DaysRemaining** — atlikušais dienu skaits pirms pašreizējās Office licences derīguma beigām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2187">**DaysRemaining** – Number of days remaining before the current Office license expires</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2188">**LicenseId** — lietotājam izsniegtās licences burtciparu identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2188">**LicenseId** – An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2189">**LicenseType** — lietotāja izmantotās Office licences veids</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2189">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingofficeclientlicensingdolicensevalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2190">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2190">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2191">Tie ir licencēšanas metadati, kas tiek apkopoti no ierīces katrā sāknēšanas reizē, kas ziņo licences ACID, licences statusu, veidu un citus licences rekvizītus, kas ir kritiski svarīgi, lai identificētu līdzekļus, kas ir iestatīti kā pieejami lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2191">This is licensing metadata that is collected from the device on every boot that reports the license acid, license status, type and other properties of the license that are critical in identifying the features set available to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2192">Tas ir kritiski svarīgi, lai identificētu līdzekļu kopu, kas ir pieejama lietotājam, un vai lietotājam trūkst kāda funkcionalitāte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2192">This is critical in identifying the feature set available to the user and if any functionality is missing for the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2193">Tas tiek izmantots arī dienas aktīvo lietotāju/mēneša aktīvo lietotāju aprēķiniem un dažādām citām atskaitēm, ko izmanto dažādas grupas sistēmā Office, jo tas norāda tipa produktu, ko lietotājs izmanto, vai tas ir abonementa produkts un vai tam trūkst kāda kritiski svarīga funkcionalitāte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2193">It is also used for Daily active users/Monthly active user calculations and various other reports by various teams across Office as this tells the type product that the user is using, whether it is a subscription product and whether they are missing any critical functionality.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2194">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2194">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2195">**FullValidationMode** — režīms, kas norāda, ka veicam pilnīgu licences verifikācijas pārbaudi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2195">**FullValidationMode** – Mode indicating that we are in full validation of license verification</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2196">**IsRFM** — norāda, vai lietotājam ir samazinātas funkcionalitātes līmenis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2196">**IsRFM** – Indicates whether the user is in reduced functionality mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2197">**IsSCA** — norāda, vai strādājam koplietojamā datora aktivizācijas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2197">**IsSCA** – Indicates whether we are running in Shared computer activation mode</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2198">**IsSubscription** — norāda, vai lietotājs izmanto abonementa licenci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2198">**IsSubscription** – Indicates whether the user is using a subscription license or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2199">**IsvNext** — norāda, vai izmantojam jauno moderno licencēšanas steku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2199">**IsvNext** – Indicates whether we are using the new modern licensing stack or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2200">**LicenseCategory** — lietotāja izmantotās Office licences kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2200">**LicenseCategory** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2201">**LicenseStatus** — lietotāja izmantotās Office licences statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2201">**LicenseStatus** – Status of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2202">**LicenseType** — lietotāja izmantotās Office licences veids</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2202">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2203">**LicensingACID** — GUID identifikators, kas norāda Office produktu, kuram lietotājam ir licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2203">**LicensingACID** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2204">**OlsLicenseId** — lietotājam izsniegtās licences burtciparu identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2204">**OlsLicenseId** - An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2205">**SkuIdIsNull** — norāda, vai radās kļūda un nezinām produktu, ko lietotājs izmanto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2205">**SkuIdIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered an error and don't know the product that the user is running</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2206">**SlapiIsNull** — norāda, vai radās problēma, aizpildot kādu licencēšanas objektu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2206">**SlapiIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered a problem in populating one of the licensing objects</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingonlinerepair"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2207">Office.Licensing.OnlineRepair</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2207">Office.Licensing.OnlineRepair</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2208">Ja kāda iemesla dēļ nevaram aktivizēt lietotāju un tam ir jārāda dialogs, kurā tiek lūgts pāriet tiešsaistē un mēģināt veikt labošanas darbības, tiek aktivizēts šis notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2208">If we are not able to activate a user for some reason and have to show them a dialog that asks them to go online and try repair steps, this event is fired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2209">Tas ir kritiski svarīgs, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam netrūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2209">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2210">Šis notikums neapkopo laukus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2210">This event collects no fields.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingoobetrybuychoice"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2211">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2211">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2212">Lietotāji, kuriem ir sākotnēji instalēta sistēma Office jaunos datoros, kuriem nav tiesību uz Office, tiek parādīts dialoglodziņš, ar ko viņi var izmēģināt, iegādāties vai ievadīt produkta kodu, lai saņemtu licenci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2212">Users with pre-installed Office on new machines who have no Office entitlement are shown a dialog through which they can try, buy or enter a product key to get licensed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2213">Šis notikums ietver lietotāja darbību dialoglodziņā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2213">This event captures the user action on the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2214">Šis notikums tiek lietots, lai izsekotu lietotāja darbību, kas tiek veikta, kad tiek parādīts dialoglodziņš lietotājiem, kuriem nav Office tiesību, kur sistēma Office tika sākotnēji instalēta datorā, un tas palīdz noteikt, vai lietotājs ir licencēts vai nelicencēts, izmantojot noformēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2214">This event is used to track the user action taken on the dialog shown to users with no Office entitlement where Office was pre-installed on the machine and helps determining if the user is licensed or unlicensed by design.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2215">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2215">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2216">**Buy** — norāda, vai lietotājs noklikšķināja uz pogas iegādāties vai nē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2216">**Buy** - Tells if the user clicked on the buy button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2217">**ForceAutoActivate** — norāda, vai ir jāveic vai nav jāveic programmas aktivizācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2217">**ForceAutoActivate** - Tells if in-app activation should be attempted or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2218">**GoBackToSignIn** — norāda, vai lietotājs vēlas pierakstīties vēlreiz (iespējams, ar citu kontu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2218">**GoBackToSignIn** - Tells if the user wanted to sign in again (possibly with another account)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2219">**IsPin** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ievadījis PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2219">**IsPin** - Tells if the user entered a pin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2220">**ProductKey** — norāda, vai lietotājs mēģināja ievadīt produkta kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2220">**ProductKey** - Tells if the user tried to enter a product key</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2221">**Try** — norāda, vai lietotājs noklikšķināja uz pogas izmēģināt vai nē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2221">**Try** - Tells if the user clicked on the try button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2222">**UserDismissed** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir noraidīja dialogu, un tāpēc būtu pagarinātas vai samazinātas funkcionalitātes režīmā, jo viņi neizvēlas iegādāties Office vai saņemt izmēģinājumversiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2222">**UserDismissed** - This tells if the user dismissed the dialog and thus would be in grace or reduced functionality mode because they didn't choose to buy office or get a trial</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingpurchase"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2223">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2223">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2224">*[Šis notikums ir dzēsts jaunākajos Office būvējumos, taču, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2224">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2225">Veicam eksperimentu, kas lietotājam sniedz iespēju izmēģināt un iestatīt automātisko maksāšanu par Office tieši no lietojumprogrammas, neizejot no lietojumprogrammas konteksta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2225">We have an experiment that gives the user an option to try and set up autopay for Office directly from an app without ever leaving the context of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2226">Tas ziņo par šī eksperimenta sekmīgu izpildi vai kļūmi kopā ar kļūdas kodu. Tas ir kritiski svarīgi, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam netrūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2226">This reports the success or failure of that experiment along with the error code It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2227">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2227">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2228">**StorePurchaseStatus** — atspoguļo pirkuma izsaukuma, kas tika veikts, izmantojot Windows Store, kļūdas kodu/sekmīgas izpildes kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2228">**StorePurchaseStatus** – Represents the error code/success code of the purchase call that was made through windows store</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingsearchforsessiontoken"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2229">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2229">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2230">Ja lietotājs strādā koplietojama datora aktivizācijas režīmā, mēs mēģinām meklēt sesijas marķieri datorā, kas lietotājam sniedz iespēju izmantot lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2230">If the user is running under shared computer activation mode, we try to search for a session token on the machine which allows the user to use the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2231">Šis notikums ziņo par scenārija sekmīgu izpildi vai kļūmi kopā ar kļūdas kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2231">This event reports the success or failure of the scenario along with the error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2232">Tas ir kritiski svarīgs, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam netrūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2232">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2233">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2233">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2234">**LoadLicenseResult** — atspoguļo kļūdas kodu/sekmīgas izpildes kodu attiecībā uz to, vai spējām ielādēt licences pašreizējam lietotājam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2234">**LoadLicenseResult** – Represents the error code/success code of whether we were able to load the licenses for the current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2235">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** — norāda, vai mēģinājām atjaunot lietotāja sesijas marķieri oportūnistiski</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2235">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates whether we attempted to renew the user's session token opportunistically</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2236">**SetAcidResult** — atspoguļo kļūdas kodu/sekmīgas izpildes kodu attiecībā uz to, vai spējām iestatīt ACID uz paredzēto vērtību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2236">**SetAcidResult** – Represent the error code/success code of whether we were able to set the acid to the expected value</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingshownewdeviceactivationdialog"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2237">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2237">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2238">Office lietojumprogrammas pirmajā sāknēšanas reizē mēs mēģināsim rādīt pierakstīšanās dialogu, kas iepriekš aizpildīts ar akreditācijas datiem, ko lietotājs izmantojat, lai lejupielādētu Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2238">On the first boot of an Office app, we will try to show a sign in dialog pre-populated with the credentials the user employed to download Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2239">Lietotājs pēc tam var turpināt pierakstīšanos ar šiem akreditācijas datiem, izmantot citus akreditācijas datus vai noraidīt dialogu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2239">The user can then continue to sign-in with those credentials, use different credentials or dismiss the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2240">Šis notikums ziņo par lietotāja veikto darbību, kad tiek parādīts šis dialogs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2240">This event reports the action taken by the user when presented with this dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2241">Tas ir kritiski svarīgi, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī modernajā licencēšanas stekā, kas tiek izmantots sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2241">It is critical for detecting if a user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2242">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2242">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2243">**UserAction** — lietotāja veiktās darbības, kad tiek parādīts šis dialogs, identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2243">**UserAction** – Identifier for the action taken by the user when presented with the dialog.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingskutoskuconversion"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2244">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2244">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2245">Licencējot lietotāju, ja mums ir jāmaina lietotāja SKU uz citu, mēs izsūtām šo signālu kopā ar sekmīgas izpildes vai kļūmes kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2245">As part of licensing the user, if we have to change the user's SKU from one SKU to another, we send this signal out along with the success or failure code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2246">Tas ir kritiski svarīgs, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam trūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2246">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2247">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2247">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2248">**DestinationSku** — tās SKU nosaukums, uz kuru pašlaik instalētais produkts ir jākonvertē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2248">**DestinationSku** – Name of the SKU to which the currently installed product should be converted to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2249">**PendingAcid** — tā produkta ID, kam ir nepabeigta SKU konvertēšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2249">**PendingAcid** – ID of the product for which a SKU conversion is pending</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2250">**SourceSku** — sākotnējās SKU, kas tika instalēta datorā, nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2250">**SourceSku** – Name of the original SKU that was installed on the machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2251">**UninstallProduct** — norāda, vai vecais produkts konvertēšanas ietvaros tiks atinstalēts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2251">**UninstallProduct** – Indicates whether the old product will be uninstalled as part of the conversion</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowolsresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2252">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2252">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2253">Kad lietotājs ir nelicencēts, mēs veicam vairākas pakalpojuma zvanus, lai lietotājam tiktu piešķirta licence, un lai aktivizētu savu Office produktu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2253">When a user is unlicensed, we make several service calls to get the user into a licensed state and to activate their Office product.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2254">Šis notikums tiek izraisīts, zvanot Office licencēšanas pakalpojumam, lai pārbaudītu, vai lietotājam ir pilnvaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2254">This event gets triggered on calling the Office Licensing Service to check if the user has entitlements.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2255">Šis pasākums tiks lietots, lai izsekotu lietotāja licencēšanas statusam pēc tam, kad tiek piezvanīts Office licencēšanas pakalpojumam un Office klienta statusam pēc mēģinājuma aktivizēt Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2255">This event is going to be used to track the user licensing health after calling the Office Licensing Service and the Office Client health after attempting to get Office activated.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2256">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2256">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2257">**EntitlementPickerShown** — norāda, vai lietotājam ir vairākas pilnvaras, un vai lietotājam bija manuāli jāizvēlas no tām, lai saņemtu licenci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2257">**EntitlementPickerShown** - Tells if the user had multiple entitlements and if the user had to manually choose from them to get licensed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2258">**GetAuthResult** — norāda dažādus stāvokļus, kādos jūsu klients var būt, piemēram, ja iegādājās tukšu produkta kodu no Office licencēšanas pakalpojuma, vai ja bija tiesības izmantot citu produktu un Office ir jāpārvērš par jauno produktu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2258">**GetAuthResult** - Tells various states the client might be in like if they got an empty product key from the Office Licensing Service or if they were entitled for another product and Office needs to be converted to the new product</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2259">**EntitlementCount** — norāda lietotājam piešķirto pilnvaru skaitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2259">**GetEntitlementsCount** - Tells the number of entitlements the user has</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2260">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** — norāda, vai zvans uz Office licencēšanas pakalpojumu API, lai izgūtu lietotāja pilnvaras, ir sekmīgs vai nē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2260">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve the user's entitlements succeeded or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2261">**GetKeySucceeded** — norāda, vai zvans uz Office licencēšanas pakalpojumu API, lai izgūtu produkta kodu, ir sekmīgs vai nē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2261">**GetKeySucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve a key succeeded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2262">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** — norāda, vai modernais licencēšanas steks varēja darboties, un vai lietotājam tika piešķirta licence vai nē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2262">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** - Tells if the modern licensing stack was able to work and if the user got licensed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2263">**InstallKeyResult** — norāda dažādus iemeslus, kāpēc lietotājs var būt sliktā stāvoklī, piemēram, ja aktivizācija neizdevās vai produkta koda instalēšana neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2263">**InstallKeyResult** - Tells various reasons why the user might be in a bad state like if activation failed or the installation of the key failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2264">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** — šis ir tikai informatīvs, un norāda, vai notikums ir pievienots telemetrijas pārvaldnieka kartei tieši nereģistrējoties</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2264">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2265">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** — šis ir tikai informatīvs, un norāda, vai tika mēģināts nosūtīt notikumu, pirms tam neveicot tiešu reģistrēšanos telemetrijas pārvaldnieka kartē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2265">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** - This is just informational and tells if the event was attempted to be sent without explicitly registering for it in the telemetry manager map before hand</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2266">**SentOnDestruction** — šis ir tikai informatīvs, un norāda, vai notikums ir pievienots telemetrijas pārvaldnieka kartei tieši nereģistrējoties un netika nosūtīts tieši</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2266">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2267">**Tag** — tiek lietota, lai iegūtu informāciju par to, kur kods ir nosūtīts no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2267">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2268">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** — norāda dažādus stāvokļus, kādos lietotājs var būt pēc tam, kad ir apstiprinātas pilnvaras, kas izgūtas no Office licencēšanas pakalpojuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2268">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** - Tells various states the user might be in after validating the entitlements retrieved from the Office Licensing Service</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowsearchforbindingresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2269">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2269">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2270">OEM pārdod iekārtas, kurās ietilpst Office (viena gada abonementi vai mūžīgi).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2270">OEMs sell machines that come with Office (one-year subscriptions or perpetual).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2271">Šie Office produkti tiek apmaksāti, kad klients iegādājas savu iekārtu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2271">These Office products are paid for when the customer purchases their machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2272">Iekārtās, kurās ir iestatīta īpaša reģistra atslēga (OOBEMode: OEMTA), iespējams, ir ar to saistīts Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2272">Machines that are set up with a specific regkey (OOBEMode: OEMTA) might have an Office binding associated with it.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2273">Kad sāknējam Office šādās iekārtās, mēs veicam pakalpojumu pārbaudes, lai noskaidrotu, vai atrasta Office saistība, kas atbilst iekārtai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2273">When we boot Office on such machines, we perform service checks to see if an Office binding corresponding to the machine is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2274">Šīs telemetrijas darbības izseko veiksmes un neveiksmes punktus, meklējot sasaisti, lai mēs varētu nodrošināt, ka iekārtas, kurās ir sasaiste, var tos veiksmīgi ienest, un šie pakalpojumi ir darbspējīgi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2274">This telemetry activity tracks the success and failure points in searching for a binding so that we can ensure that machines that do have a binding can successfully fetch them, and that our services are healthy.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2275">Šī darbība neizseko iekārtas, kuriem nav saistījumu ar tām pēc tam, kad esam pārbaudījuši ar saviem pakalpojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2275">This activity does not track machines that turn out to not have any bindings associated with them after we check with our services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2276">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2276">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2277">**DexShouldRetry** — signāls, ka esam saskārušies ar atkārtojuma problēmu (internets vai serveri nedarbojas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2277">**DexShouldRetry** - Signal that we’ve hit a retryable issue (no internet or servers are down)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2278">**GenuineTicketFailure** — norāda kļūmi HRESULT, kas rodas, mēģinot iegūt iekārtas Windows orģināla biļeti/produkta atslēgu (WPK).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2278">**GenuineTicketFailure** - Tells us the failure HRESULT when trying to get the machine's Windows genuine ticket/product key (WPK).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2279">**PinValidationFailure** — norāda, kāpēc PIN validācijas process neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2279">**PinValidationFailure** - Tells us why the pin validation process failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2280">Iespējamās kļūdas:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2280">Possible errors:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2281">GeoBlocked</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2281">GeoBlocked</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2282">InvalidFormat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2282">InvalidFormat</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2283">InvalidPin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2283">InvalidPin</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2284">InvalidState</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2284">InvalidState</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2285">InvalidVersion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2285">InvalidVersion</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2286">Unknown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2286">Unknown</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2287">Used</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2287">Used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2288">**PinValidationResult** — norāda PIN validācijas rezultātu, ko neizdevās atkost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2288">**PinValidationResult** - Tells us the pin validation result of a pin that we failed to crack.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2289">**Pkpn** — Pkpn diapazons, kuram pieder PIN.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2289">**Pkpn** - The pkpn range that the pin belongs to.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2290">**Success** — norāda, ka mēs sekmīgi ienesām derīgu Office piesaisti (PIN) iekārtai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2290">**Success** - Indicates that we successfully fetched a valid Office binding (pin) for the machine.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2291">**Tag** — norāda, kurā solī apstājāmies meklēt sasaistīšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2291">**Tag** - Tells us at which step we stopped searching for a binding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2292">Iespējamie tagi:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2292">Possible tags:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2293">0x03113809  nav interneta savienojuma/pakalpojuma kļūdas, pārbaudot PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2293">0x03113809    No internet/service error while validating pin</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2294">0x0311380a PIN validācijas kļūme, nosūtīta ar PinValidationFailure lauku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2294">0x0311380a    Pin validation failure, sent with PinValidationFailure field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2295">0x0310410f  izdevās, nosūtīts ar panākumu lauku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2295">0x0310410f    Success, sent with Success field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2296">0x0311380d  kļūdu novēršana (interneta problēmas, nezināmas kļūdas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2296">0x0311380d    Retry-able errors (internet issues, unknown errors)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2297">0x0311380e  neiespējamu atkārtotu mēģinājumu kļūdas (saistošais piedāvājums beidzies)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2297">0x0311380e    Non-retry-able errors (binding offer expired)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2298">0x0311380f   citas kļūdas (nav iespējams licencēt)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2298">0x0311380f    Other errors (unable to license)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2299">0x03104111  neizdevās atkost Office PIN, kas nosūtīts ar PinValidationResult lauku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2299">0x03104111    Failed to crack the Office pin, sent with PinValidationResult field</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2300">**WpkBindingFailure** — norāda kļūdas kodu, lai iegūtu Office PIN, kas saistīts ar ierīces WPK.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2300">**WpkBindingFailure** - Tells us the error code of getting the Office pin bound to the machine's WPK.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowafodialogs"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2301">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2301">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2302">Pēc sekmīgas Office PIN iegūšanas, kas ir saistīts ar iekārtu un iepriekš sasaistīts ar Office, mēs parādīsim lietotājam pierakstīšanās dialogu vai izpirkšanas dialogu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2302">After successfully obtaining a valid Office pin bound to a machine pre-bundled with Office, we show the user either a sign-in dialog or a redemption dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2303">Kad PIN kods ir izpirkts, tiek parādīts dialoglodziņš EULA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2303">Once the pin is redeemed, we show the EULA dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2304">Kā daļu no mūsu modernizācijas AFO līdzekļa mēs atsvaidzinājām abus dialogus, lai sniegtu papildinformāciju par Office produktu, kas ir komplektā ar iekārtu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2304">As a part of our modernizing AFO feature, we refreshed the two dialogs to convey more information regarding the Office product that comes with the machine.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2305">Šie telemetrijas dati seko, ja mūsu līdzeklis sekmīgi samazina lietotāju neērtības, izsekojot izpirkšanas procesa plūsmas un iziešanas punktus (kurš dialoglodziņš ir noraidīts).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2305">This telemetry is to track if our feature successfully reduces user friction in redeeming their product by tracking the flow and exit points of the redemption process (which dialog was dismissed).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2306">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2306">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2307">**ActionActivate** — signāls, ko lietotājs ir noklikšķinājis uz pogas “Activate” (Aktivizēt).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2307">**ActionActivate** - Signal that user clicked the “Activate” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2308">**ActionChangeAccount** — signāls, ka lietotājs ir noklikšķinājis uz hipersaites “Use a different account” (Izmantot citu kontu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2308">**ActionChangeAccount** -  Signal that user clicked the “Use a different account” hyperlink.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2309">**ActionCreateAccount** — signāls, ka lietotājs ir noklikšķinājis uz pogas “Create account” (Izveidot kontu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2309">**ActionCreateAccount** - Signal that user clicked the “Create account” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2310">**ActionSignIn** — signāls, ka lietotājs ir noklikšķinājis uz pogas “Sign in” (Pierakstīties).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2310">**ActionSignIn** - Signal that user clicked the “Sign in” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2311">**CurrentView** — tā dialoga tips, kuru lietotājs aizvēris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2311">**CurrentView** - The type of dialog the user closed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2312">**DialogEULA** — signāls, kas parādīja dialogu ‘Accept EULA’ (Akceptēt EULA).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2312">**DialogEULA** -  Signal that we showed the ‘Accept EULA’ dialog.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2313">**DialogRedemption** — signāls, kas parādīja AFO izpirkšanas dialogu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2313">**DialogRedemption** - Signal that we showed the AFO redemption dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2314">**DialogSignIn** — signāls, kas parādīja AFO pierakstīšanās dialogu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2314">**DialogSignIn** - Signal that we showed the AFO sign-in dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2315">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** — signāls, ka nav izdevies saņemt noklusējuma izpirkšanas informāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2315">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** - Signal that we failed to fetch default redemption information.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2316">**GetRedemptionInfo** — signāls, ka tiek iegūta demogrāfiskā informācija par PIN izpirkšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2316">**GetRedemptionInfo** - Signal that we’re fetching demographic information for pin redemption.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2317">**MalformedCountryCode** — signāls, ka valsts kods, kas nepieciešams PIN izpirkšanai, ir nepareizs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2317">**MalformedCountryCode** - Signal that the country code needed for pin redemption is malformed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2318">**OExDetails** — detalizēta informācija par kļūdu, kas tiek atgriezta, kad tiek noraidīts identitātes pierakstīšanās dialogs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2318">**OExDetails** - The error details we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2319">**OExType** — detalizēta informācija par kļūdu, kas tiek atgriezta, kad tiek noraidīts identitātes pierakstīšanās dialogs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2319">**OExType** - The error type we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2320">**Tag** — norāda, kurā solī lietotājs iziet no AFO izpirkšanas procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2320">**Tag** - Tells us at which step the user exits the AFO redemption process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2321">Iespējamie tagi:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2321">Possible tags:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2322">0x0311380b    lietotājs noraidīja identitātes pierakstīšanās dialoglodziņu no izpirkšanas dialoglodziņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2322">0x0311380b    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2323">0x0311380c    neizdevās automātiski ielādēt identitāti pēc lietotāja pierakstīšanās no izpirkšanas dialoglodziņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2323">0x0311380c    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2324">0x03113810    neizdevās ielādēt konta demogrāfisko informāciju (valsts kodu, valodu, valūtu, izmēģinājuma piedāvājumu un mārketinga preferences)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2324">0x03113810    Failed to load the account's demographic information (country code, language,     currency, trial offer, and marketing preferences)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2325">0x03113805    lietotājs noraidīja identitātes pierakstīšanās dialoglodziņu no pierakstīšanās dialoglodziņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2325">0x03113805    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2326">0x03113806    neizdevās automātiski ielādēt identitāti pēc lietotāja pierakstīšanās no pierakstīšanās dialoglodziņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2326">0x03113806    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2327">0x03113807    neizdevās automātiski ielādēt identitāti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2327">0x03113807    Failed to auto-load an identity</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2328">0x03113811    lietotājs aizvēra dialoglodziņu pierakstīšanās/izpirkšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2328">0x03113811    User closed the sign-in/redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2329">0x03113812    lietotājs aizvēra akceptēt EULA dialoglodziņu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2329">0x03113812    User closed the accept EULA dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2330">0x03113808    lietotājs akceptēja EULA līgumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2330">0x03113808    User accepted the EULA</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2331">0x03113811      lietotājs aizvēra dialogu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2331">0x03113811      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2332">0x2370e3a0      lietotājs aizvēra dialogu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2332">0x2370e3a0      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2333">0x2370e3c1      doties uz tīmekli, lai saņemtu PIN izpirkšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2333">0x2370e3c1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2334">0x2370e3a1      doties uz tīmekli, lai saņemtu PIN izpirkšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2334">0x2370e3a1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2335">0x2370e3c0      dialoga secība tika cikliski atkārtota, ko izraisa lietotājs, pārejot uz priekšu un atpakaļ dialogā plūsma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2335">0x2370e3c0      Dialog sequence looped caused by user going back and forth in the dialog flow</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2336">0x2370e3a3      lietotājs noklikšķināja uz hipersaites “Not now” (Ne tagad), kas izlaiž AFO piedāvājumu tai sesijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2336">0x2370e3a3      User clicked “Not now” hyperlink which skips the AFO offer for that session</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2337">0x2370e3a2      lietotājs noklikšķināja uz hipersaiti “Never show this to me” (Nekad nerādīt šo iespēju), kas atspējo AFO piedāvājumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2337">0x2370e3a2      User clicked on “Never show this to me” hyperlink which disables the AFO offer</span></span>


- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2338">**UseInAppRedemption** — norāda mums, vai mēs palīdzam lietotājiem programmā izpirkšanai vai nosūtīšanai uz tīmekļa vietni, lai izmantotu to ienesto PIN (iepriekš aizpildītu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2338">**UseInAppRedemption** - Tells us if we're keeping users in-app for redemption or sending them to the web to redeem their fetched pin (pre-populated).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2339">**UseModernAFO** — norāda mums, vai izmantojat jauno vai veco AFO pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2339">**UseModernAFO** - Tells us if we're using the new or old AFO experience.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowtrybuydialogforoobe"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2340">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2340">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2341">Kad jaunās iekārtās ir instalēts Office, bet lietotājam nav pilnvaru, tiek parādīts dialoglodziņš, kurā lietotājam tiek piedāvāts izmēģināt, iegādāties vai ievadīt produkta kodu, lai lietotājs varētu saņemt licenci, un šis notikums seko, vai tiek parādīts dialoglodziņš.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2341">When new machines have Office pre-installed and the user doesn't have an entitlement we show a dialog which gives the user the option to try, buy or enter a product key so that the user can get licensed and this event tracks if the dialog was shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2342">Šis pasākums palīdzēs saprast, vai dialoglodziņš bija redzams lietotājam, lai izmēģinātu, iegādātos vai ievadītu produkta kodu, un tādējādi palīdzēs mums noteikt, vai lietotājam bija iespēja saņemt licenci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2342">This event will help with knowing if the dialog was shown to the user to try, buy or enter the product key and hence will help us determine if the user had the opportunity to get licensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2343">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2343">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2344">**ActiveView** — norāda lietotājam redzamā dialoglodziņa ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2344">**ActiveView** - Tells the dialog ID shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2345">**CurrentOOBEMode** — norāda pirmsinstalēšanas režīmu (OOBE režīmu, piemēram, AFO, OEM u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2345">**CurrentOOBEMode** - Tells the pre-install mode (OOBE mode such as AFO, OEM etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2346">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** — šis ir tikai informatīvs, un norāda, vai notikums ir pievienots telemetrijas pārvaldnieka kartei tieši nereģistrējoties</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2346">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2347">**SentOnDestruction** — šis ir tikai informatīvs, un norāda, vai notikums ir pievienots telemetrijas pārvaldnieka kartei tieši nereģistrējoties un netika nosūtīts tieši</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2347">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2348">**ShowTryButton** — norāda, vai izmēģināšanas poga bija redzama lietotājam dialoglodziņā vai nē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2348">**ShowTryButton** - Tells if the Try Button was shown to the user on the dialog or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2349">**Tag** — tiek lietota, lai iegūtu informāciju par to, kur kods ir nosūtīts no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2349">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowtrialflow"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2350">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2350">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2351">Ja lietotājs ar nelicencētu Office, kas iepriekš ir instalēts iekārtā, mēģina saņemt izmēģinājumversiju, tiek aktivizēts šis notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2351">When an unlicensed user of Office pre-installed on a machine is attempting to get a trial, this event gets triggered.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2352">Tas tiek izmantots, lai redzētu, kurš lietotājs sekos, lai saņemtu izmēģinājumversiju, un vai rodas kļūdas, mēģinot saņemt izmēģinājumversiju, izmantojot programmas pirkumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2352">It is used to see which path the user would follow to get a trial and if there were any errors while getting the trial through in-app purchases.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2353">Atkarībā no lietotāja darbības un programmas iegādes rezultāta lietotājs var netikt licencēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2353">Depending on the user action and the result of the in-app purchase the user could end up being unlicensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2354">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2354">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2355">**HasConnectivity** — norāda, vai lietotājam ir interneta savienojums, un gadījumā, ja lietotājam nav, iespējams, ir jāizmanto pagarinājuma licence piecu dienu laikā, vai, iespējams, darbojas samazinātas funkcionalitātes režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2355">**HasConnectivity** - Tells if the user has internet connectivity and in case there isn't the user might have to use a grace license for five days or may be in reduced functionality mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2356">**InAppTrialPurchase** — norāda, vai ir iespējots lidojums veikala iegādes SDK palaišanai, lai tvertu PI un iegādātos izmēģinājumversiju programmā *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2356">**InAppTrialPurchase** - Tells if the flight is enabled for launching the Store Purchase SDK to capture PI and purchase a trial from within the application *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2357">**IsRS1OrGreater** — norāda, vai operētājsistēmas versija ir lielāka par RS1 vai nav, jo veikala iegādes SDK ir jāizmanto tikai tad, ja OS versija ir lielāka RS1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2357">**IsRS1OrGreater** - Tells if the OS Version is greater than RS1 or not since the Store Purchase SDK should be used only if the OS Version is greater that RS1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2358">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** — tikai informatīvs, un norāda, vai notikums ir pievienots telemetrijas pārvaldnieka kartei tieši nereģistrējoties</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2358">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding**: This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2359">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** — norāda, vai lidojums ir iespējots, lai nosūtītu lietotājus uz tīmekļa vietni un izpirktu izmēģinājumversiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2359">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** - Tells if the flight is enabled to send users to the web to redeem a trial</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2360">**StoreErrorConditions** — norāda dažādus nosacījumus, saskaņā ar kuriem veikalu iegādes SDK varētu neizdoties *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2360">**StoreErrorConditions** - Tells the various conditions under which the Store Purchase SDK could have failed *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2361">**StoreErrorHResult** — norāda kļūdas kodu no veikalu iegādes SDK *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2361">**StoreErrorHResult** - Tells the error code returned from the Store Purchase SDK *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2362">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** — norāda, kā tiek zvanīts veikala iegādei SDK, un, ja lietotājs ir veicis pirkumu vai nē, kas palīdzēs noteikt, vai lietotājam ir jābūt licencētam izmantot Office *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2362">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** - Tells the result of calling the Store Purchase SDK and if the user made a purchase or not which will help determine if the user should get licensed to use Office *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2363">**Tag** — tiek lietota, lai iegūtu informāciju par to, kur kods ir nosūtīts no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2363">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2364">**UserSignedInExplicitly** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir pierakstījies tieši. Šādā gadījumā mēs atkārtoti novirza lietotājus uz tīmekļa vietni izmēģinājumversijai *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiks rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2364">**UserSignedInExplicitly** - Tells if the user signed in explicitly in which case, we would re-direct users to the web for the trial *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingusegracekey"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2365">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2365">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2366">Ja kāda iemesla dēļ nevaram lietotāju licencēt, instalējam pagarinājuma atslēgu un izsūtām signālu, kas to paziņo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2366">For some reason if we are unable to license the user, we install a grace key and send out this signal that signifies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2367">Tas ir kritiski svarīgs, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī un vai tam trūkst funkcionalitātes, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2367">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2368">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2368">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2369">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** — norāda, vai mēģinājām oportūnistisku atjaunošanu lietotājam koplietojamā datora aktivizācijas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2369">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates if we attempted an opportunistic renewal for the user in shared computer activation mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2370">**ReArmResult** — norāda instalētās atslēgas atkārtotu aktivizēšanu, kas var pagarināt pašreizējās licences derīgumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2370">**ReArmResult** – Indicates the result of rearming the installed key which can extend the expiry of the current license</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteenrollmentresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2371">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2371">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2372">Šis notikums reģistrē statusu pēc Intune reģistrēšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2372">This event logs the status upon Intune enrollment.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2373">Šis scenārijs ir raksturīgs tikai Intune iespējotiem kontiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2373">This scenario is specific to Intune enabled accounts.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2374">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2374">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2377">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai uzskaitītu notikumus un izmērītu kļūdas ietekmi, kuras dēļ lietotāji šodien SKU izvēles ekrānā redz “Null” nevis cenu. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2377">This event is used to capture events to quantify the impact of the bug due to which users today see “Null” instead of a price at the SKU chooser screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2378">Šī kļūda tiks diagnosticēta, lai noteiktu tās labojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2378">The bug will be diagnosed further to determine a fix.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2379">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2379">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2380">**PriceNotFound** – veikala cena nav atrasta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2380">**PriceNotFound** - Prices is not found from the store.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2381">**StoreNotInitilized** – kad veikals netiek veiksmīgi inicializēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2381">**StoreNotInitilized** - When store is not initialized successfully.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2399">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2399">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2533">Šis notikums norāda, ka programma ir palaista.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2533">This event denotes that the application launched.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2534">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai uzskaitītu programmas, kurām MAU var kontrolēt atjauninājumus, pieejamo kopiju skaitu, kā arī to versiju un instalācijas atrašanās vietu (noklusējuma vai cita).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2534">We use this event to list the applications for which MAU can control updates, the number of copies available as well as their version and install location (default or other).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2538">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2538">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2540">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2540">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2541">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2541">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2542">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2542">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2543">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2543">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2546">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2546">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2557">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2557">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2621">Šis notikums reģistrē problēmas ar instalēšanu klonā (t.i., vai nu neizdodas izveidot savienojumu ar palīgu, lai lietotu atjauninājumu, vai savienojums ir izveidot, bet palīgs nevar lietot atjauninājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2621">This event records issues with install on clone (i.e. either we fail to connect to the helper to apply an update, or we connect but the helper is unable to apply the update).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2622">Ja tiek ziņots par kādu ierakstu, tas nozīmē, ka instalēšana klonā neizdevās un ka tagad ir jāveic atkāpšanās uz atjauninājumu atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2622">If we ever get a record reported, this means install on clone has failed and will now have to fall back to an in-place update.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2626">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2626">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2627">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2627">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2628">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2628">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2629">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2629">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2630">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2630">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2631">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2631">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2632">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2632">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2633">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2633">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2634">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2634">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2635">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2635">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

### <a name="cloningtaskstatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2641">cloningtask.status</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2641">cloningtask.status</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2642">Šis notikums norāda uz programmas, kas tiks atjaunināta, klonēšanas procesa statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2642">This event indicates status of cloning process for the application to be updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2643">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu sekmīgas izpildes reižu skaitu un kļūdu, kas izraisa kļūmes, tipus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2643">We use this event to determine success rate as well as types of errors encountered causing failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2644">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, vai klonēšanas līdzeklis ir jāierobežo dažādos auditorijas kanālos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2644">This event is used to determine whether cloning feature should be throttled on different audience channels.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2645">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2645">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2646">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2646">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2647">**AppID** — programmas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2647">**AppID** - The application identifier.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-2648">**AppInfo_Language** — valoda, kurā darbojas programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-2648">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-3787">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-3787">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-3803">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-3803">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-3805">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-3805">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-3812">**Payload** — norāda, vai kļūda ir pielāgotā servera iestatījumos vai instalētajos MAU komponentos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-3812">**Payload** -Indicates whether error lies with custom server setup, or installed MAU components</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4136">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4136">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4137">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4137">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4138">**AppID** — programmas, kas tiek atjaunināta, identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4138">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4139">**AppInfo_Language** — valoda, kurā darbojas programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4139">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4140">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4140">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4141">**BundleVersion** — programmas, kas tiek atjaunināta, versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4141">**BundleVersion** - Version of the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4142">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4142">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4143">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4143">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4144">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4144">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4145">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4145">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4146">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4146">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4147">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4147">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4148">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4148">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4149">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4149">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4150">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4150">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4151">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4151">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4152">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** — IP adreses pirmie trīs okteti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4152">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first three octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4153">**PreviousUpdateID** — programmas atjauninājuma identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4153">**PreviousUpdateID** - Identifier for an application update</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4154">**SessionId** — sesijas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4154">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4155">**UpdateID** — programmas atjauninājuma identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4155">**UpdateID** - Identifier for an application update</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4156">**UpdatePkg** — instalējamās atjauninājuma pakotnes nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4156">**UpdatePkg** - Name of the update package being applied</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4157">**UpdateVersion** — programmas versija pēc atjauninājuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4157">**UpdateVersion** - Version of the application after the update</span></span>


### <a name="downloadtaskdownloadfailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4158">downloadtask.downloadfailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4158">downloadtask.downloadfailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4159">Šis notikums reģistrē to, ka pakotnes faila lejupielādes laikā radās kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4159">This event logs that an error occurred downloading a package file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4160">Reģistrējam atjauninājuma ceļu un kļūdu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4160">We log the update path and the error.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4161">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu paredzēto atjaunināšanas procesa darbību un lai palīdzētu novērst kļūdas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4161">We use this event for ensuring the update process works as expected and to help troubleshoot errors.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4162">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4162">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
