- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4164">**AppID** — programmas, kurai ir lejupielādes kļūme, identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4164">**AppID** – The identifier of application that has download failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4165">**AppInfo_Language** — valoda, kurā darbojas programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4165">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4166">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4166">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4167">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4167">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4168">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4168">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4169">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4169">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4170">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4170">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4171">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4171">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4172">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4172">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4173">**Error** — lejupielādes laikā novērotā kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4173">**Error** – The error observed during download.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4174">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4174">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4175">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4175">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4176">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4176">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4177">**HowTocheck** — pārbaudes, vai nav atjauninājumu, preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4177">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4178">**Payload** — satur lejupielādējamā atjauninājuma nosaukumu un novēroto kļūdu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4178">**Payload** - Contains the name of the update being downloaded and the error observed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4179">*[Šis lauks ir dzēsts jaunākajos Office būvējumos, taču, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4179">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4180">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4180">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4181">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** — IP adreses pirmie 3 okteti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4181">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4182">**SessionId** — sesijas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4182">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4183">**UpdateID** — lejupielādējamā atjauninājuma identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4183">**UpdateID** – The identifier of the update being downloaded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4491">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4491">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4492">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4492">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4536">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4536">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4541">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4541">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4598">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4598">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4884">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4884">**Device_NetworkCountry** – The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4885">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4885">**DeviceID** – The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4886">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4886">**DeviceInfo_Model** – The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-4892">**HowTocheck** — pārbaudes, vai nav atjauninājumu, preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-4892">**HowTocheck** – The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5537">Šis notikums ziņo par to, ka programma tika palaista, kad tā tika atjaunināta, un Microsoft AutoUpdate pārtrauc palaistās programmas darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5537">This event reports that an application was launched while it was being updated, and Microsoft AutoUpdate is terminating the launched application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5538">Ņemiet vērā, ka programmas palaišana, kad tā tiek atjaunināta, var izraisīt programmas bojājumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5538">Note that launching an application while being updated may result in application corruption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5539">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu to, ka atjaunināšanas procesu neietekmē palaistā programma pirms tā ir gatava lietošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5539">We use this event to ensure update process is not impacted by launched application before it is ready to be used.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5540">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5540">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5541">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5541">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5542">**AppID** — atjaunināšanas laikā palaistās programmas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5542">**AppID** - The identifier of application that was launched during updates.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5543">**AppInfo_Language** — valoda, kurā darbojas programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5543">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5544">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5544">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5545">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5545">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5546">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5546">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5547">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5547">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5548">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5548">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5549">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5549">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5550">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5550">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5609">Notikums norāda, ka pagaidu faili, kas tika izveidotie programmas instalēšanas laikā tika veiksmīgi notīrīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5609">This event indicates temporary files created during application installation were successfully cleaned up.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5610">Tas veido daļu no atjauninājuma piltuves, kas tiek izmantota programmu darbspēju noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5610">This forms part of update funnel used to determine application update health.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5611">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5611">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5728">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5728">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5729">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5729">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5732">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5732">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5733">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5733">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5735">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5735">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5737">**HowTocheck** — pārbaudes, vai nav atjauninājumu, preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5737">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

### <a name="installedappacknowledgedcoreappleevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5764">installedapp.acknowledgedcoreappleevent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5764">installedapp.acknowledgedcoreappleevent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5765">Šis notikums norāda, ka Microsoft Auto Update (MAU) saņēma Apple notikuma apstiprinājumu no reģistrētas lietojumprogrammas, lai izbeigtu lietojumprogrammas darbību, lai turpinātu gaidošās lietojumprogrammas atjaunināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5765">This event indicates Microsoft Auto Update (MAU) has received an Apple event acknowledgment from a registered application to terminate the application to proceed with pending application update.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5766">Šis notikums pašlaik tiek izmantots, lai palīdzētu izstrādāt uzlabojumus nākotnē, kas samazinātu lietotāju traucēšanu programmu atjaunināšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5766">This event is used to help develop future enhancement to minimize user interruption during application updates.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5767">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5767">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5768">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5768">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5769">**AppID** — programmas, kas tiek atjaunināta, identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5769">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5770">**AppInfo_Language** — valoda, kurā darbojas programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5770">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5771">**AppleEventClass** — norāda notikuma, kas tiek nosūtīts/apstiprināts, tipu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5771">**AppleEventClass** - Indicates type of event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5772">**AppleEventID** — notikuma, kas tiek nosūtīts/apstiprināts, unikālais identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5772">**AppleEventID** - Unique identifier for the event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5773">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5773">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5774">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5774">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5775">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5775">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5776">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5776">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5777">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5777">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5778">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5778">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5779">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5779">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5780">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5780">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5781">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5781">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5782">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5782">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5783">**HowToCheck** — kā pārbaudīt iestatījumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5783">**HowToCheck** - How to check setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5784">**Payload** — satur atkārtoto mēģinājumu skaitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5784">**Payload** - Contains retry count</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5785">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5785">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5786">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** — IP adreses pirmie 3 okteti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5786">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5787">**SessionId** — sesijas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5787">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5788">**UpdateID** — atjauninājuma identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5788">**UpdateID** - The update identifier</span></span>

### <a name="installedappsendcoreappleevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5873">installedapp.sendcoreappleevent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5873">installedapp.sendcoreappleevent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5874">Šis notikums norāda, ka Microsoft Auto Update (MAU) nosūta Apple notikumu uz reģistrētu programmu, lai izbeigtu programmas darbību, lai turpinātu gaidošo programmas atjaunināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5874">This event indicates Microsoft Auto Update (MAU) is sending an Apple event to a registered application to terminate the application in order to proceed with pending application update.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5875">Šis notikums pašlaik tiek izmantots, lai palīdzētu izstrādāt uzlabojumus nākotnē, kas samazinātu lietotāju traucēšanu programmu atjaunināšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5875">This event is currently being used to help develop future enhancement to minimize user interruption during application updates.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5876">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5876">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5877">**Acknowledged** — norāda, vai attiecīgā programma apstiprināja notikuma saņemšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5877">**Acknowledged** - Indicates whether the subject application has acknowledged receipt of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5878">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5878">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5879">**AppID** — programmas, kas tiek atjaunināta, identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5879">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5880">**AppInfo_Language** — valoda, kurā darbojas programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5880">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5881">**AppleEventClass** — norāda notikuma, kas tiek nosūtīts/apstiprināts, tipu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5881">**AppleEventClass** - Indicates type of event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5882">**AppleEventID** — notikuma, kas tiek nosūtīts/apstiprināts, unikālais identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5882">**AppleEventID** - Unique identifier for the event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5883">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5883">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5884">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5884">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5885">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5885">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5886">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5886">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5887">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5887">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5888">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5888">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5889">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5889">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5890">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5890">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5891">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5891">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-5892">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-5892">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-6932">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-6932">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8066">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8066">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8075">**HowTocheck** — pārbaudes, vai nav atjauninājumu, preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8075">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

### <a name="webserviceswhatsnew"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8251">webservices.whatsnew</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8251">webservices.whatsnew</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8258">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8258">**Channel** -The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8259">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8259">**Device_NetworkCountry** -The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8260">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8260">**DeviceID** -The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8261">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8261">**DeviceInfo_Model** -The hardware model of the device</span></span>

## <a name="onenote-sync-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8272">OneNote sinhronizācijas notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8272">OneNote sync events</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8273">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8273">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8274">Šis notikums reģistrē piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizācijas rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8274">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8275">Tas tiek lietots, lai, aprēķinot OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, noteiktu, cik daudz ir unikālu sinhronizācijas mērķu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8275">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8276">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8276">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8277">**CachedError_Code** A— numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8277">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8278">**CachedError_Description** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8278">**CachedError_Description** – a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8279">**CachedError_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8279">**CachedError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8280">**CachedError_Type** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8280">**CachedError_Type** – the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8281">**ExecutionTime** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai replicētu piezīmju grāmatiņu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8281">**ExecutionTime** – time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8282">**Gosid** — globālais objektu telpas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8282">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8283">**IdentityType** — identitātes tips, piemēram, Windows Live, organizācijas ID utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8283">**IdentityType** – identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8284">**InitialReplicationInSession** — norāda, vai šī replicēšana ir pirmā piezīmju grāmatiņas replicēšana pēc atvēršanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8284">**InitialReplicationInSession** – is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8285">**IsBackgroundSync** — norāda, vai tā ir fona sinhronizācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8285">**IsBackgroundSync** – is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8286">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda tiek apspiesta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8286">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8287">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda ir neparedzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8287">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8288">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda tiek apspiesta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8288">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8289">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda ir neparedzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8289">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8290">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai sadaļu sinhronizācijas kļūdas tiek apspiestas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8290">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8291">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūda bija paredzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8291">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8292">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizēšana notiek, izmantojot moderno lapas satura sinhronizāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8292">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8293">**LastAttemptedSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņu tika mēģināts sinhronizēt iepriekšējo reizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8293">**LastAttemptedSync** – timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8294">**LastBackgroundSync** — laikspiedols, kad notika pēdējais mēģinājums veikt sinhronizāciju fona režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8294">**LastBackgroundSync** – timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8295">**LastNotebookViewedDate** — datums, kad piezīmju grāmatiņa pēdējoreiz tika skatīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8295">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8296">**LastSuccessfulSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņa iepriekš sekmīgi sinhronizēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8296">**LastSuccessfulSync** – timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8314">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8314">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8315">Šis notikums reģistrē WebSocket sinhronizācijas rezultātu gan OneNote modernā lapas satura sinhronizācijai, gan modernās hierarhijas sinhronizācijai. Tas tiek lietots, lai, aprēķinot OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, noteiktu, cik daudz ir unikālu sinhronizācijas mērķu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8315">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8316">Tas tiek izmantots arī OneNote modernās sinhronizācijas veiktspējas informācijas paneļa vajadzībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8316">It is also used for OneNote modern sync performance dashboard.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8317">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8317">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8318">**CloseReason** — WebSocket aizvēršanas iemesls, piemēram, anormāla aizvēršana utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8318">**CloseReason** - WebSocket close reason, e.g. Abnormal close, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8319">**DataIsFreshCount** — sekmīgo atgādāšanas pieprasījumu skaits WebSocket sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8319">**DataIsFreshCount** - number of successful pull requests in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8320">**DeviceSessionId** — ierīces sesijas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8320">**DeviceSessionId** - Device session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8321">**DownloadCount** — lejupielāžu skaits WebSocket sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8321">**DownloadCount** - number of downloads in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8322">**Error** — tas pamatā ir Exception_Type+Exception_Description+Exception_Code+Exception_Tag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8322">**Error** - is basically Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8323">**Exception_Code** — numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8323">**Exception_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8324">**Exception_Description** — kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8324">**Exception_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8325">**Exception_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8325">**Exception_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8326">**Exception_Type** — kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8326">**Exception_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8327">**FirstUpdateSize** — pirmā atjaunināšanas ziņojuma garums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8327">**FirstUpdateSize** - first update message length</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8328">**HasError** — norāda, vai WebSocket sesijas laikā radās kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8328">**HasError** - whether there is an error during the WebSocket session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8329">**IsEducationNotebook** — norāda, vai pašreizējā piezīmju grāmatiņa ir piezīmju grāmatiņa izglītības iestādēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8329">**IsEducationNotebook** - Is the current notebook education notebook or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8330">**IsHierarchyResource** — norāda, vai pašreizējais resurss ir lapa vai sadaļa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8330">**IsHierarchyResource** - Is the current resource a page or a section</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8331">**NotebookId** — OneNote piezīmju grāmatiņas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8331">**NotebookId** - OneNote notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8332">**OperationWithError** — kuras operācijas laikā notika kļūda, piemēram, WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8332">**OperationWithError** - in which operation did the error happen, e.g. WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8333">**ResourceId** — OneNote lapas vai sadaļas resursa ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8333">**ResourceId** - OneNote page or section resource ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8334">**SectionId** — OneNote sadaļas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8334">**SectionId** - OneNote section ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8335">**ServerSessionId** — sesijas ID, kas tiek izmantota savstarpējai WebSocket pieprasījuma un onenote.com saistīšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8335">**ServerSessionId** - session ID used to correlate WebSocket request to onenote.com</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8336">**SessionDurationInMs** — WebSocket sesijas ilgums milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8336">**SessionDurationInMs** - the duration in milliseconds of the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8337">**TenantId** — SharePoint nomnieka ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8337">**TenantId** - SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8338">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai saņemtu pirmo atjauninājumu no servera puses pēc tam, kad tika izveidota WebSocket sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8338">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - time in milliseconds taken to receive first update from the server side after the WebSocket session is established</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8339">**UploadAckCount** — augšupielādes apstiprinājumu skaits WebSocket sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8339">**UploadAckCount** - number of acknowledges for upload in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8340">**Web URL** — PII notīrītais tīmekļa vietrādis URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8340">**WebUrl** - PII scrubbed web URL</span></span>
