### <a name="officeonenotestoragesyncscore"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8373">Office.OneNote.Storage.SyncScore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8373">Office.OneNote.Storage.SyncScore</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8374">Šis notikums reģistrē visus lietotājiem redzamos negatīvos sinhronizācijas iespēju apstākļus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8374">This event logs all negative factors in sync experience that are visible to users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8375">Tas tiek lietots, lai aprēķinātu OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, kas ir kritisks rādītājs, novērtējot OneNote lietotāju sinhronizācijas iespējas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8375">It is used to calculate OneNote sync score, which is a critical metric to evaluate OneNote users' sync experience.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8376">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8376">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8377">**AutoShowSyncStatus** — norāda, vai sinhronizācijas statuss tiek rādīts automātiski</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8377">**AutoShowSyncStatus** - whether sync status is auto shown or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8378">**Cause** — kas izraisīja OneNote lapu/sadaļu pārvietošanu uz nesakārtotām sadaļām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8378">**Cause** - what caused OneNote pages/sections moved to misplaced sections</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8379">**Context** — uzskaitījums kategorizē, ko lietotājs cenšas veikt, piemēram, sadaļas pārdēvēšana, piezīmju grāmatiņas atkārtota atvēršana utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8379">**Context** - an enum categorizes what user is trying to do, e.g. rename a section, reopen a notebook, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8380">**Error_Code** — numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8380">**Error_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8381">**Error_Description** — kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8381">**Error_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8382">**Error_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8382">**Error_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8383">**Error_Type** — kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8383">**Error_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8384">**ErrorText** — kļūdas teksts, kas redzams lietotāja interfeisā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8384">**ErrorText** - error text shown in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8385">**Explanation** — paskaidro, kāda veida ir gaidošas izejošās izmaiņas, kas ir jāpārvieto uz nesakārtotām sadaļām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8385">**Explanation** - explains what kind of pending outbound changes that need to be moved to misplaced sections</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8386">**fishbowlType** — akvārija tips, piemēram, lapas akvārijs, sadaļas akvārijs utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8386">**fishbowlType** - type of fishbowl, e.g. page fishbowl, section fishbowl, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8387">**IDS** — lietotāja interfeisā redzamā teksta vesela skaitļa identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8387">**IDS** - an integer identifier for the text shown in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8388">**idsFishbowl** — lietotāja interfeisā redzamās akvārija kļūdas vesela skaitļa identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8388">**idsFishbowl** - an integer identifier for the fishbowl error shown in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8389">**IsUsingRealtimeHierarchySync** — norāda, vai tiek izmantota modernās hierarhijas sinhronizācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8389">**IsUsingRealtimeHierarchySync** - Is using modern hierarchy sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8390">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8390">**NotebookId** - notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8391">**PageSyncUIState** — lapas sinhronizācijas statusa virkne, piemēram, UpToDate, Syncing, SaveOffline, SyncError utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8391">**PageSyncUIState** - page sync status string, e.g., UpToDate, Syncing, SaveOffline, SyncError, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8392">**ServerGosid** — jaunizveidotās konflikta lapas resursa ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8392">**ServerGosid** - resource ID for newly created conflict page</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8393">**Source** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda, kurš notikums izraisīja UI, t.i., izveidoja jaunu redx attēlu, sinhronizācijas kļūda sinhronizācijas lietotāja interfeisā, parādīja kļūdas dialogu utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8393">**Source** - an enum indicates which event triggered the UI, i.e. created a new redx image, sync error in the sync UI, error dialog displayed, etc.</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteappprovisioningmovelocalnotebooktoonlinenotebookfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8394">OneNote.App.Provisioning.MoveLocalNotebookToOnlineNotebookFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8394">OneNote.App.Provisioning.MoveLocalNotebookToOnlineNotebookFailed</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8395">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, ja lokālās piezīmju grāmatiņas pārnešana uz disku neizdodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8395">This event is logged when move of local notebook to drive fails.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8396">Šis scenārijs attiecas uz novēlotas pierakstīšanās lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8396">This scenario is specific to delayed sign-in user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8397">Kad lietotājs pierakstās, lokālā piezīmju grāmatiņa tiek pārnesta uz viņu OneDrive krātuvi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8397">When the user signs in, their local notebook is transferred to their OneDrive storage.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8398">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8398">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8399">**ErrorMsg** — kļūdas ziņojums, kas atbilst kļūmei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8399">**ErrorMsg** - The error message corresponding to the failure.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestorageconnectivitychanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8400">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8400">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8401">Notikumu žurnāli, ja lietotājam ir vai nav savienojums ar internetu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8401">The event logs if a user has internet connectivity or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8402">Tas tiek lietots, lai saistītu citus sinhronizācijas darbspējas standartus, ļaujot mums ignorēt notikumus, kas notiek, kamēr lietotājam nav interneta savienojuma, jo nesagaidām, ka mūsu pakalpojuma latentums būs pieņemams bez interneta savienojuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8402">This is used to correlate the other sync health performance metrics by allowing us to ignore events that occur while a user does not have internet connectivity as we do not expect our service latency to be acceptable without internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8403">Tas ļauj mums aprēķināt precīzu sesiju skaitu mūsu metrikai starp klientu sektoriem (par katru nomnieku, par katru sektoru).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8403">This allows us to calculate an accurate session count for our metrics across slices of customers (per-tenant, per-sector).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8404">Mēs to izmantojam arī, lai filtrētu kļūdu ziņojumus, jo ir daudz sinhronizācijas kļūdu, kuras, iespējams, tiks rādītas bez tīkla savienojama, bet pretējā gadījumā jāveic izmeklēšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8404">We also use it to filter error reports as there are numerous sync errors that we expect to occur without network connectivity but that warrant investigation otherwise.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8405">Ja nesaņemsim šos datus, mēs nevarēsim precīzi pārraudzīt mūsu produktu veiktspēju vai noteikt, vai ir paredzams, ka lietotājam radušās kļūdas, vai arī jums būs jāveic papildu izmeklēšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8405">If we do not receive this data, we will not be able to accurately monitor our products performance or determine if errors experienced by a user are expected or require further investigation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8406">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8406">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8407">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** — ja savienojuma stāvoklis ir mainīts, lai tagad tas būtu internets</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8407">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** -  If the connectivity state has been changed so it is now Internet</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyinboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8408">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8408">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8409">Svarīgo signālu izmanto, lai izsekotu ienākošo sinhronizācijas darbību veiktspēju, kuras tieši mijiedarbojas ar SharePoint, ieskaitot sasaistīto informāciju, kas ļauj mums pārraudzīt un izmeklēt datu augšupielādes veiktspēju mūsu pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8409">The critical signal used to track the performance of inbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8410">Šis signāls apkopo tikai sliktākās veiktspējas lejupielādes pēdējās 300 sekundēs (sekunžu skaitu Microsoft var konfigurēt atkarībā no pakalpojuma veiktspējas un nosacījuma).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8410">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8411">Tas tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu pakalpojumu darbspēju, ļaujot mums redzēt, kuri nomnieki saskaras ar nepieņemami lēnu datu saņemšanu mūsu pakalpojumā, informāciju par datiem, ko tie augšupielādē, kad tieši rodas palēnināta saņemšana, un to, cik izplatīta ir latentuma problēma nomnieku vidū.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8411">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data to our service, information about the data they are uploading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8412">Tas tiek izmantots, lai ziņotu par pakalpojumu darbspēju un veiktspēju mūsu klientiem, lai novērtētu tendences laika gaitā un brīdinātu par problēmām, kas automātiski attiecas uz inženiertehnisko mazināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8412">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8413">Ja mums nav šo datu, tas neļaus mums nodrošināt atbilstošu lejupielādes veiktspēju, kad lietotājs sinhronizēs izmaiņas no SharePoint savā datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8413">If we do not have this data it will prevent us from ensuring adequate download performance when a user syncs changes from SharePoint to their computer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8414">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8414">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8415">**IsEducationNotebook** — Būls, kas norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņa ir piezīmju grāmatiņa izglītības iestādēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8415">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8416">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8416">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8417">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams augšupielādes veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8417">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyoutboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8418">OneNote.Storage.LegacyOutboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8418">OneNote.Storage.LegacyOutboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8419">Svarīgo signālu izmanto, lai izsekotu izejošo sinhronizācijas darbību veiktspēju, kuras tieši mijiedarbojas ar SharePoint, ieskaitot sasaistīto informāciju, kas ļauj mums pārraudzīt un izmeklēt datu augšupielādes veiktspēju mūsu pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8419">The critical signal used to track the performance of outbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8420">Šis signāls apkopo tikai sliktākās veiktspējas lejupielādes pēdējās 300 sekundēs (sekunžu skaitu Microsoft var konfigurēt atkarībā no pakalpojuma veiktspējas un nosacījuma).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8420">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8421">Tas tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu pakalpojumu darbspēju, ļaujot mums redzēt, kuri nomnieki saskaras ar nepieņemami lēnu datu nosūtīšana mūsu pakalpojumā, informāciju par datiem, ko tie augšupielādēja, kad tieši rodas palēnināta nosūtīšana, un to, cik izplatīta ir latentuma problēma nomnieku vidū.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8421">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow outbound of data to our service, information about the data they were uploading when they experienced the slow outbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8422">Tas tiek izmantots, lai ziņotu par pakalpojumu darbspēju un veiktspēju mūsu klientiem, lai novērtētu tendences laika gaitā un brīdinātu par problēmām, kas automātiski attiecas uz inženiertehnisko mazināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8422">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8423">Ja mums nav šo datu, tas neļaus mums nodrošināt atbilstošu veiktspēju, sinhronizējot lietotāju izmaiņas no SharePoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8423">If we do not have this data, it will prevent us from ensuring adequate performance when syncing users changes up to SharePoint.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8424">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8424">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8425">**IsEducationNotebook** — Būls, kas norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņa ir piezīmju grāmatiņa izglītības iestādēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8425">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8426">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8426">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8427">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams augšupielādes veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8427">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimefiledataobjectdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8428">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8428">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8429">Svarīgo signālu izmanto, lai izsekotu veiktspēju, ja lietotājs saņem faila datu objektu (piemēram, iegultu failu vai attēlu), kas ir lejupielādēts tieši no mūsu pakalpojuma, nevis kā daļa no sinhronizācijas operācijas lapā, sadaļā vai piezīmju grāmatiņā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8429">The critical signal used to track performance when a user inbounds a file data object (i.e. an embedded file or image) which is downloaded directly from our service and not as part of a sync operation on a page, section or notebook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8430">Šis signāls apkopo tikai sliktākās veiktspējas lejupielādes pēdējās 300 sekundēs (sekunžu skaitu Microsoft var konfigurēt atkarībā no pakalpojuma veiktspējas un nosacījuma).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8430">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8431">Tas tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu pakalpojumu darbspēju un veiktspēju, ļaujot mums redzēt, kuri nomnieki saskaras ar nepieņemami lēnu lejupielādi no mūsu pakalpojuma, un cik izplatīta ir latentuma problēma nomnieku vidū, un ziņo par mūsu uzvedību laika gaitā, ļaujot mums izmērīt pakalpojumu veiktspējas tendences.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8431">This is used to ensure service health and performance by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow download of data from our service, and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is, and report our behavior over time allowing us to measure service performance trends.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8432">Ja ir novērojams nepieļaujams latentums faila objektam, tiks izmantoti arī šie dati, lai savstarpēji saistītu ar citiem signāliem no klienta un pakalpojuma, kas attiecas uz šo objektu, lai uzlabotu mūsu lejupielādes procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8432">If we see an unacceptable latency for a file object, we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the object to make improvements to our download process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8433">Mēs arī sadalījām datus, pamatojoties uz lejupielādētā failu objekta paplašinājumu, jo mums ir dažādas gaidas, pamatojoties uz to, vai fails tiek prezentēts mūsu kanvā (piem., attēls), vai arī tas ir fails, kas nav ievietots (piemēram, teksta dokuments).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8433">We also split the data based on the extension of the file object downloaded as we have different expectations based on whether the file is presented inline in our canvas (e.g. an image) or is a non-inline file (such as a text document).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8434">Ja nesaņemsim šos datus, mēs nevarēsim pārraudzīt šo lejupielāžu veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8434">If we do not receive this data, it will prevent us from monitoring the performance of these downloads</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8435">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8435">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8436">**FileSizeInBytes** — lejupielādētā faila lielums baitos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8436">**FileSizeInBytes** - The size of the file being downloaded in bytes</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8437">**IsImage** — Būla noteikšana, ja lejupielādējamajam failam ir paplašinājums, kas atbilst iepriekš noteiktam bieži lietotā attēla formātu (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png) sarakstam, kas tiek rādīts iekļautajā kanvā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8437">**IsImage** - A bool determining if the file being downloaded has an extension that matches a pre-determined list of common image formats (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png) that we display inline in the canvas</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8438">**TimeToDownload** — laiks, kas bija nepieciešams, lai veiksmīgi lejupielādētu FDO no mūsu BLOB krātuves ierīcē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8438">**TimeToDownload** - The length of time it took to successfully download the FDO from our blob storage to the device</span></span> 

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8439">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8439">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8440">Svarīgo signālu izmanto, lai izsekotu ienākošo sinhronizācijas darbību veiktspēju, ieskaitot sasaistīto informāciju, kas ļauj mums pārraudzīt un izmeklēt datu lejupielādes no mūsu pakalpojuma (onenote.com) veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8440">The critical signal used to track performance of inbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of downloading data from our service (onenote.com).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8441">Šis signāls apkopo tikai sliktākās veiktspējas lejupielādes pēdējās 300 sekundēs (sekunžu skaitu Microsoft var konfigurēt atkarībā no pakalpojuma veiktspējas un nosacījuma).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8441">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8442">Tas tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu pakalpojumu darbspēju, ļaujot mums redzēt, kuri nomnieki saskaras ar nepieņemami lēnu datu saņemšanu no mūsu pakalpojuma, informāciju par datiem, ko tie lejupielādēja, kad tieši rodas palēnināta saņemšana, un to, cik izplatīta ir latentuma problēma nomnieku vidū.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8442">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data from our service, information about the data they were downloading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8443">Tas tiek izmantots, lai ziņotu par pakalpojumu darbspēju un veiktspēju mūsu klientiem, lai novērtētu tendences laika gaitā un brīdinātu par problēmām, kas automātiski attiecas uz inženiertehnisko mazināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8443">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8444">Ja sadaļai vai piezīmju grāmatiņai tiek novērots nepieņemams latentums, mēs izmantosim arī šos datus, lai saistītu ar citiem signāliem no klienta un pakalpojuma, kas attiecas uz to pašu dokumentu, lai identificētu klienta puses veiktspējas regresijas, kas ļauj mums nodrošināt labākas veiktspējas pakalpojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8444">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify client-side performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8445">Ja nesaņemsim šos datus, mēs nevarēsim pārraudzīt šī mūsu pakalpojuma darbības rezultātu vai servera puses izmaiņu ietekmi, kas, iespējams, ir nepieciešama lietošanas vai citu faktoru dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8445">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8446">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8446">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8447">**DeviceSessionId** — ierīces sesijas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8447">**DeviceSessionId** -  The ID of the device session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8448">**IsEducationNotebook** — Būls, kas norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņa ir piezīmju grāmatiņa izglītības iestādēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8448">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8449">**IsHierarchyResource** — Būls, kas norāda, vai resurss ir hierarhijas resurss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8449">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8450">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8450">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8451">**ResourceId** — resursa ID, kuru augšupielādējam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8451">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8452">**SectionId** — sadaļas ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8452">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8453">**ServerSessionId** — servera ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8453">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8454">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** — laiks milisekundēs starp lietotāju, kurš pārvietojas uz lapu, un replicēšanas steku, kas apstiprina, ka šī lapa ir sinhronizēta ar serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8454">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds between a user navigating to a page and the replication stack confirming that page is in sync with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8455">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** — laiks milisekundēs starp sinhronizācijas programmu, kas sākas ar lapas ienākošo replicēšanu, un replicēšanas darbību, kura sasniegusi sinhronizāciju ar servera stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8455">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - The time in milliseconds between the sync engine beginning inbound replication of a page and that replication operation reaching the in sync with the server state.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8456">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8456">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8457">Svarīgo signālu izmanto, lai izsekotu izejošo sinhronizācijas darbību veiktspēju, ieskaitot sasaistīto informāciju, kas ļauj mums pārraudzīt un izmeklēt datu augšupielādes mūsu pakalpojumā (onenote.com) veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8457">The critical signal used to track the performance of outbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service (onenote.com)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8458">Tas tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu pakalpojumu darbspēju, ļaujot mums redzēt, kuri nomnieki saskaras ar nepieņemami lēnu datu nosūtīšana mūsu pakalpojumā, informāciju par datiem, ko tie augšupielādēja, kad tieši rodas palēnināta nosūtīšana, un to, cik izplatīta ir latentuma problēma nomnieku vidū.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8458">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow outbound of data to our service, information about the data they were uploading when they experienced the slow outbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8459">Tas tiek izmantots, lai ziņotu par pakalpojumu darbspēju un veiktspēju mūsu klientiem, lai novērtētu tendences laika gaitā un brīdinātu par problēmām, kas automātiski attiecas uz inženiertehnisko mazināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8459">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8460">Mēs arī izmantosim šos datus, lai izsekotu mūsu klientu un pakalpojumu uzlabojumu ietekmi un efektivitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8460">We will also use this data to track the impact and effectiveness of improvements we make to our clients and services.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8461">Ja sadaļai vai piezīmju grāmatiņai tiek novērots nepieņemams latentums, mēs izmantosim arī šos datus, lai saistītu ar citiem signāliem no klienta un pakalpojuma, kas attiecas uz to pašu dokumentu, lai identificētu veiktspējas regresijas, kas ļauj mums nodrošināt labākas veiktspējas pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8461">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8462">Ja nesaņemsim šos datus, mēs nevarēsim pārraudzīt šī mūsu pakalpojuma darbības rezultātu vai servera puses izmaiņu ietekmi, kas, iespējams, ir nepieciešama lietošanas vai citu faktoru dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8462">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8463">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8463">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8464">**DeviceSessionId** — ierīces sesijas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8464">**DeviceSessionId** - The ID of the device session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8465">**IsEducationNotebook** — Būls, kas norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņa ir piezīmju grāmatiņa izglītības iestādēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8465">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8466">**IsHierarchyResource** — Būls, kas norāda, vai resurss ir hierarhijas resurss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8466">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8467">**IsWorstTime** — Būls, kas norāda, vai laiks ir regulārs augšupielādes notikums, vai vissliktākais laiks, ko novērojām šim klientam pēdējās 300 sekundēs (sekunžu skaitu var konfigurēt Microsoft atkarībā no pakalpojuma veiktspējas un nosacījuma).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8467">**IsWorstTime** - A bool indicating if the time is a regular upload event, or the worst time we saw on this client in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8468">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8468">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8469">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** — laiks, kad pakalpojums ir pateicis klientam par ieteicamo iestatīto intervālu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8469">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** - The time the service has communicated to the client as its recommended put interval</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8470">**ResourceId** — resursa ID, kuru augšupielādējam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8470">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8471">**SectionId** — sadaļas ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8471">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8472">**SenderRequestId** — sūtītāja ID, kas veic augšupielādi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8472">**SenderRequestId** - The ID of the sender performing the upload</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8473">**ServerSessionId** — servera ID, kas ir daļa no šīs augšupielādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8473">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8474">**UploadNonSuspendedTimeInMs** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams augšupielādes veikšanai, izņemot laiku, kad lietojumprogramma tika apturēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8474">**UploadNonSuspendedTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload excluding the time when the application was suspended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8475">**UploadTimeInMs** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams augšupielādes reālai veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8475">**UploadTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to actually perform the upload</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8476">**WaitTimeInMs** — laiks milisekundēs starp augšupielādes pieprasīšanu un augšupielādes sākšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8476">**WaitTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds between an upload being requested and an upload starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8477">**WebURL** — augšupielādes tīkls URL (Pieteicies kā PiiWz)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8477">**WebUrl** - The WebUrl of the upload (Logged as a PiiWz)</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragesynchealth"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8478">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8478">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8479">Svarīgo signālu izmanto, lai izsekotu kļūdas un izņēmumus, kas ir radušies sinhronizācijas stekā OneNote klientā, kas ļauj mums pārraudzīt un mazināt šādus neparedzētus nosacījumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8479">The critical signal used to track errors and exceptions that have occurred inside the sync stack in the OneNote client allowing us to monitor and mitigate these unexpected conditions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8480">Tas tiek lietots, lai nodrošinātu pakalpojuma darbspēju, ļaujot mums skatīt klientu kļūdu ziņojumus reāllaikā, un ļauj mums reaģēt uz sinhronizācijas problēmām tiklīdz tās rodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8480">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see error reports from the clients in near real time, which lets us respond to sync issues as they arise.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8481">To izmanto arī, lai noteiktu, cik izplatīta ir problēma, un cik nopietna ir, savstarpēji norādot kļūdas atzīmi ar klienta kodu, lai identificētu kļūmes avotu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8481">It is also used to identify how widespread an issue is, and how severe by cross-referencing the error tag with the client code to identify the source of failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8482">Mēs apkopojām arī šos datus, lai iegūtu informāciju par mūsu veiktspēju laika gaitā un to uzlabojumu ietekmi un efektivitāti, ko veicam saviem klientiem un pakalpojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8482">We also aggregate this data to get information on our performance over time and the impact and effectiveness of improvements we make to our clients and services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8483">Ja mums nav šo datu, mēs nevarēsim proaktīvi reaģēt uz kļūdu nosacījumiem mūsu sinhronizācijas pakalpojumā, bez klienta eskalācijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8483">If we do not have this data, we won’t be able to proactively respond to error conditions in our sync service without customer escalation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8484">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8484">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8485">**Service** — sinhronizācijas pakalpojums, ko klients izmantoja, kad radās kļūda (mantotā vai modernā sinhronizācija)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8485">**Service** - The sync service the client was using when the error occurred (Legacy or Modern Sync)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8486">**Tag** — atzīme (identifikācijas vērtība), kura norāda kļūdu, kas radās sinhronizācijas darbības laikā klientam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8486">**Tag** - The tag (an identifying value) representing the error that the client encountered during the sync operation</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesynccreatenotebookfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8487">OneNote.Sync.CreateNotebookFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8487">OneNote.Sync.CreateNotebookFailed</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8488">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, ja neizdodas izveidot piezīmju grāmatiņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8488">This event is logged when creation of a notebook fails.</span></span>  
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8489">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8489">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8490">**NetworkConnection** — reģistrē savienojuma tipu, kurā ierīce pašlaik ir ieslēgta, piemēram, Wi-Fi, bezsaistē, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8490">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8491">**ServerType** — reģistrē servera tipu, kur tiks izveidota piezīmju grāmatiņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8491">**ServerType** - Logs the server type where notebook was to be created.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesyncfirstrunerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8492">OneNote.Sync.FirstRunError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8492">OneNote.Sync.FirstRunError</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8493">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, ja lietotājam, veicot pirmās palaišanas darbības ierīcē, neizdevās sinhronizēt ātrās piezīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8493">This event is logged when syncing of Quick Notes failed for a user during their First Run Experience on a device.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8494">Šis ir raksturīgs pirmās palaišanas scenārijam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8494">This is specific to the First Run scenario.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8495">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8495">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8496">**NetworkConnection** — reģistrē savienojuma tipu, kurā ierīce pašlaik ir ieslēgta, piemēram, Wi-Fi, bezsaistē, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8496">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8497">**ServerType** — reģistrē servera tipu, kur tiks izveidota ātro piezīmju grāmatiņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8497">**ServerType** - Logs the server type where Quick Notes notebook was to be created</span></span>

## <a name="services-configuration-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8498">Pakalpojumu konfigurācijas notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8498">Services Configuration events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8499">Pakalpojumu konfigurācija neapkopo nepieciešamos pakalpojumu datu notikumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8499">No required service data events are collected by Services Configuration.</span></span>

## <a name="telemetry-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8500">Telemetrijas notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8500">Telemetry events</span></span>

### <a name="appdeeplink"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8501">app.deep.link</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8501">app.deep.link</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8502">Šis notikums palīdz izsekot kalendāra sapulču palaišanu dažādos gala punktos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8502">This event helps to track the usage of calendar meeting launch, across different endpoints.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8503">Šis notikums ļauj mums noteikt, vai sapulce tiek palaista no Skype darbam, un tad, kad sapulce tiek palaista no Teams, un, vai lietojumprogramma Teams ir instalēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8503">This event lets us detect two things when a meeting is launched via Skype for Business, and when a meeting is launched via Teams, and if the Teams app is installed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8504">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8504">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8505">**account** — hešotā konta, kas veica darbību, informāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8505">**account** - Hashed account information which performed the action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8506">**action_type** – veiktās darbības veids, piemēram, sapulces palaišana vai lietojumprogrammas instalēšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8506">**action_type** - action performed, such as launch meeting or install application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8507">**application** – lietojumprogramma, kas tika palaista ar dziļo saiti, piemēram, Teams vai Skype darbam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8507">**application** - Application that was launched via a deep link, such as Teams or Skype for Business</span></span>


### <a name="officeandroiddocsuipaywallcontrolpaywalloperationmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8508">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.PaywallOperationMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8508">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.PaywallOperationMetrics</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroiddocsuipaywallcontrolpaywallsessiondata"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8515">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.PaywallSessionData</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8515">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.PaywallSessionData</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8516">*[Šī notikuma iepriekšējais nosaukums bija Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PaywallSessionData.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8516">*[This event was previously named Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PaywallSessionData.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8517">Sesijas metadati, kad lietotājam tiek parādīts Paywall lietotāja interfeiss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8517">Session-based metadata when Paywall UI is shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8518">Microsoft izmanto šo opciju, lai iegūtu lietotāja pieredzi un saprastu ierīces un operētājsistēmas versijas, ko lietotājs izmanto, lai palīdzētu pieņemt lēmumus par investīcijām, lai uzlabotu pieredzi šajos apgabalos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8518">Microsoft uses this to get the user journey, and understand the device and OS versions the user is using, to help make decisions on investments in improving the experience in these areas.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8519">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8519">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8520">**App Version** — patērējošās lietojumprogrammas versijas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8520">**App Version** - Version code of the consuming application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8521">**ClientId** — anonīms identifikators, kas nav PII unikāls ierīces identifikators (GUID/virkne)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8521">**ClientId** - Anonymous non-PII unique device identifier (guid / string)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8522">**Entry Point** — unikāls kontekstuālo vai nemainīgo ievadīšanas punktu identifikators no patērējošās lietojumprogrammas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8522">**Entry Point** - Unique identifier for contextual or constant entry points from the consuming application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8523">**isTablet** — vai ierīcē tiek rādīts planšetdators UX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8523">**isTablet** - Whether the device is showing tablet UX</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8524">**OSVersion** — ierīces Android OS versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8524">**OSVersion** - Android OS version of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8525">**SessionId** — GUID: unikāls Paywall sesijas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8525">**SessionId** - Guid: Unique Paywall session identifier</span></span>


### <a name="officefirstrunappletelemetryoptin"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8526">Office.FirstRun.Apple.TelemetryOptIn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8526">Office.FirstRun.Apple.TelemetryOptIn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8531">**Data_EventId** – kods, kas norāda lietotāja atlasītu diagnostikas datu vākšanas preferenci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8531">**Data_EventId** – A code indicating the diagnostic data collection preference selected by the user.</span></span>

### <a name="officeiospaywallprovisioningresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8532">Office.iOS.Paywall.Provisioning.Response</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8532">Office.iOS.Paywall.Provisioning.Response</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8533">Produktu telemetriju, kas tiek izmantoti, lai saistītu pirkumu darbību informāciju ar Microsoft tirdzniecības sistēmu un iespējotu saistīto abonementu priekšrocības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8533">Product telemetry used for reconciliation of purchase transaction information with the Microsoft commerce system to enable associated subscription benefits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8534">Izmanto, lai atvieglotu darījumu reģistrēšanu un abonēšanas nodrošināšanu turpmākai uzziņai un iekšējai saskaņošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8534">Used to facilitate the transaction logging and subscription provisioning for future reference and internal reconciliation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8535">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8535">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8536">**entryPoint** — virkne — poga/plūsma, no kuras tika parādīts Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8536">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8537">Piemēram, “Premium jaunināšanas poga” vai “Pirmās palaišanas plūsma”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8537">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8538">**failureReason** — virkne — tiek pievienota tikai tad, ja statuss ir "kļūme".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8538">**failureReason** - String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8539">Norāda kļūdas reakciju, ko sniedz RFS nodrošināšanas atbilde.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8539">Indicating the error response given by the RFS Provisioning response.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8540">**productId** — virkne — lietojumprogrammas veikala pieprasītā produkta ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8540">**productId** - String – App Store ID of the product the request was made for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8541">**status** — virkne — veiksme vai kļūme, norādot, vai pieprasījums ir izdevies vai nav izdevies</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8541">**status** - String – Success or Failure, indicating if the request succeeded or failed</span></span>


### <a name="officeiospaywallstorekitresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8542">Office.iOS.Paywall.StoreKit.Response</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8542">Office.iOS.Paywall.StoreKit.Response</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8543">Dati tiek apkopoti kā kritiski tehniskās telemetrijas dati, lai reģistrētu pirkšanas mēģinājuma rezultātus, ko lietotājs aktivizējis manuāli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8543">The data is collected as critical engineering telemetry to log the result of purchase attempt triggered manually by user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8544">Produktu telemetrija tiek izmantota, lai saistītu pirkumu darbību informāciju ar Microsoft tirdzniecības sistēmu un iespējotu saistīto abonementu priekšrocības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8544">The product telemetry is used for reconciliation of purchase transaction information with the Microsoft commerce system to enable associated subscription benefits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8545">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8545">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8546">**entryPoint** — virkne — poga/plūsma, no kuras tika parādīts Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8546">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8547">Piemēram, “Premium jaunināšanas poga” vai “Pirmās palaišanas plūsma”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8547">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8548">**failureReason** — virkne — tiek pievienota tikai tad, ja statuss ir "kļūme".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8548">**failureReason** - String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8549">Norāda kļūdas reakciju, ko sniedz lietojumprogrammu veikala atbilde.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8549">Indicating the error response given by the App-store response</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8550">**productId** — virkne — tikai "MakePurchase", "PendingPurchase", tā produkta ID lietojumprogrammu veikalā, par kuru tiek iesniegts pieprasījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8550">**productId** - String – Only for “MakePurchase”, “PendingPurchase”, the app-store ID of the product for which the request was made.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8551">**productsCount** — Int — tikai "ProductsFetch" — veikalā atgriezto produktu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8551">**productsCount** - Int – Only for “ProductsFetch”, the number of products returned by Store.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8552">**requestType** — virkne — StoreKit pieprasījuma tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8552">**requestType** - String – Type of StoreKit request.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8553">Piemēram, "ProductsFetch", "PendingPurchase"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8553">Like “ProductsFetch”, “PendingPurchase”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8554">**status** — virkne — sekmīga izpilde vai kļūme, norādot pieprasījuma veiksmīgumu vai kļūmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8554">**status** - String – Success or Failure, indicating success or failure of the request</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotegetsharepointidsfordocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8555">Office.OneNote.GetSharePointIdsForDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8555">Office.OneNote.GetSharePointIdsForDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8556">Apkopotie dati reģistrē SharePoint (SPO) ID sekmīgu vai nesekmīgu iegūšanu dokumenta vietrādim URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8556">The data collected logs the failure and success of fetching the SharePoint (SPO) IDs for a document URL.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8557">Izsaukuma sekmīga vai nesekmīga izpilde (tai skaitā nesekmīgas izpildes iemesls) tiek reģistrēta visām platformām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8557">The success and the failure (including the reason for failure) of the call is logged for all platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8558">Šis marķieris ir nepieciešams, lai sekotu un diagnosticētu ID saņemšanai veiktā izsaukuma darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8558">This marker is required to track and diagnose the health of the call made to get the IDs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8559">ID ir nepieciešami, lai OneNote lapas (daļa no SharePoint saglabātajām piezīmju grāmatām) dati tiktu rādīti plūsmā.  </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8559">The IDs are required to have a OneNote page (belonging to SharePoint-stored notebooks) data displayed in the feed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8560">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8560">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8561">**ErrorCode** — kļūdas int vērtība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8561">**ErrorCode** - int value of error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8562">**ErrorMessage** — kļūdu aprakstošā virkne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8562">**ErrorMessage** - string describing error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8563">**FailureType** — kļūdas tipa noteikšanai paredzētā virkne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8563">**FailureType** - string to determine type of error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8564">**HttpStatusCode** — tīkla izsaukuma HTTP kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8564">**HttpStatusCode** - HTTP error code for network call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8565">**InnerErrorCode** — int kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8565">**InnerErrorCode** - int code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8566">**InnerErrorMesage** — kļūdas ziņojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8566">**InnerErrorMesage** - message for error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8567">**IsSuccess** — Būla vērtība, ja signāls ir sekmīgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8567">**IsSuccess** - Boolean value for is signal succeeded</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8574">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8574">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemgracefulexitgracefulappexitdesktop"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8582">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8582">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8583">Notikumu izraisa atbilstoša Office klienta programmu izbeigšana, piemēram, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook un citas programmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8583">The event is triggered by a graceful application termination for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8584">Mēs izmantojam rādītāju Atbilstoša izbeigšana, lai novērtētu Office klienta produktu darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8584">We use Graceful Exit to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-8585">Tas ir paredzēts kā uzņēmējdarbībai svarīgs signāls, kuru izmanto Office inženieri, lai noteiktu produktu stabilitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-8585">It is intended to be a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsystemhealthungracefulappexitimmersive"></a><span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9071">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulAppExitImmersive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9071">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulAppExitImmersive</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9072">Tiek izmantots, lai tvertu avāriju metriku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9072">Used to capture crash metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9073">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9073">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9074">**AffectedProcessAppBuild —** būvējuma versijas identifikators ietekmētajam procesam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9074">**AffectedProcessAppBuild -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9075">**AffectedProcessAppBuildRevision —** būvējuma pārskatījuma identifikators ietekmētajam procesam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9075">**AffectedProcessAppBuildRevision -** Build revision identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9076">**AffectedProcessAppMajorVer —** būvējuma galvenās versijas identifikators ietekmētajam procesam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9076">**AffectedProcessAppMajorVer -** Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9077">**AffectedProcessAppMinorVer —** būvējuma papildversijas identifikators ietekmētajam procesam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9077">**AffectedProcessAppMinorVer -** Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9078">**AffectedProcessAppName —** ietekmētā procesa nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9078">**AffectedProcessAppName -** The name of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9079">**AffectedProcessExeBuildVersion —** ietekmētā procesa būvējuma versijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9079">**AffectedProcessExeBuildVersion -** The Build Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9080">**AffectedProcessExeMajorVersion —** ietekmētā procesa galvenās versijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9080">**AffectedProcessExeMajorVersion -** The Major Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9081">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion —** ietekmētā procesa papildversijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9081">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion -** The Minor Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9082">**AffectedProcessExeRevisionVersion —** ietekmētā procesa būvējuma pārskatījuma versijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9082">**AffectedProcessExeRevisionVersion -** The Build Revision Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9083">**AffectedProcessIsDebug —** vai ietekmētais process ir atkļūdošanas būvējums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9083">**AffectedProcessIsDebug -** Whether the affected process is a debug build.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9084">**AffectedProcessIsLabMachine —** vai ietekmētais process ir Microsoft laboratorijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9084">**AffectedProcessIsLabMachine -** Whether the affected process is in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9085">**AffectedProcessOsEnvironment —** ietekmētā procesa operētājsistēmas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9085">**AffectedProcessOsEnvironment -** An operating system identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9086">**AppName —** ietekmētās lietojumprogrammas nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9086">**AppName -** The name of the affected application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9087">**CrashedAssignedFlights —** avarējušajam procesam piešķirtie lidojumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9087">**CrashedAssignedFlights -** The flights assigned to the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9088">**CrashedConfigIds —** avarējušajam procesam piešķirtā konfigurācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9088">**CrashedConfigIds -** The configuration assigned to the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9089">**CrashedImpressionId —** avarējušā procesa seansa identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9089">**CrashedImpressionId -** The impression identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9090">**CrashedInteractionSessionID —** mijiedarbības sesijas identifikators ietekmētajam procesam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9090">**CrashedInteractionSessionID -** The interaction session identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9091">**CrashedInteractionSessionTime —** laiks, kad ar ietekmēto procesu var mijiedarboties.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9091">**CrashedInteractionSessionTime -** The time when the affected process could be interacted with.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9092">**CrashedProcessSessionID —** avarējušā procesa unikāls identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9092">**CrashedProcessSessionID -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9093">**CrashedProcessSessionInitTime —** laiks, kad ietekmētais process tika sākts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9093">**CrashedProcessSessionInitTime -** The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9094">**DetectionTime —** laiks, kad tika konstatēta neparedzētā izeja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9094">**DetectionTime -** The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9095">**IsLabMachine —** vai sistēma Office tiek izmantota Microsoft laboratorijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9095">**IsLabMachine -** Whether Office is being run in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9096">**IsMsftInternal —** vai Windows lietotājs, kurš izmanto Office, ir Microsoft darbinieks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9096">**IsMsftInternal -** Whether the Windows user running Office is a Microsoft employee.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9101">Notikumu izraisa abnormāla lietojumprogrammas apture (piemēram, likvidēts uzdevumu pārvaldnieks, uzkaras programma utt.) Office klienta programmām, ieskaitot, bet ne tikai, Word, Excel, PowerPoint un Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9101">The event is triggers by an abnormal application termination (for example, task manager kill, application hang, etc.) for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9102">Mēs izmantojam rādītājus par nelabvēlīgu iziešanu no programmas, lai mērītu Office klienta produktu darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9102">We use Ungraceful Application Exit metrics to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9103">Tas ir uzņēmējdarbībā svarīgs signāls, kuru izmanto Office inženieri, lai noteiktu produktu stabilitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9103">It is a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9104">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9104">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9193">**CrashedProcessSessionId —** avarējušā procesa unikāls identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9193">**CrashedProcessSessionId -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9194">**CrashType —** avārijas veida intervāla identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9194">**CrashType -** Bucketing identifier for the type of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9196">**ExceptionAddress —** adrese programmā, kur kļūme radās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9196">**ExceptionAddress -** Address in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9197">**ExceptionCode —** izņēmuma intervāla identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9197">**ExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9205">**ModuleName —** kļūdainā moduļa nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9205">**ModuleName -** Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9206">**ModuleOffset —** nobīde baitos no bāzes adreses, kur kļūme radās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9206">**ModuleOffset -** Offset in bytes from the base address where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9207">**ModuleSize —** kļūdainā moduļa izmērs baitos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9207">**ModuleSize -** Failing module size in bytes.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9208">**OSEnvironment —** identifikators, kādā vidē Office darbojas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9208">**OSEnvironment -** Identifier for what environment Office is running on.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9210">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime —** laiks, kad iepriekšējā mijiedarbības sesija tika sākta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9210">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime -** Time which the previous interaction session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9211">**PreviousLifecycleState —** iepriekšējās sesijas dzīves cikla stāvokļa identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9211">**PreviousLifecycleState -** Previous session lifecycle state identifier.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9212">**PreviousSessionInitTime —** laiks, kad iepriekšējā sesija tika sākta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9212">**PreviousSessionInitTime -** Time when the previous session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9213">**StackHash —** identifikators, kas norāda, kur kodā ietekmētais process avarēja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9213">**StackHash -** An identifier indicating where in code that the affected process crashed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="dfdfe-9497">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfdfe-9497">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
